ra%20Modi%20with%20bemusement%20as%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fmodi-at-scindia-school-heaps-praise-on-jyotiraditya-his-father-8994260%2F%5C%22%3Eshowered%20effusive%20praise%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20his%20new%20found%20%3Cem%3Edamadji%3C%2Fem%3E.%20After%20all%2C%20praise%20from%20the%20prime%20minister%20never%20augured%20well%2C%20they%20said.%20Nevertheless%2C%20Union%20aviation%20minister%20Jyotiraditya%20Scindia%20glowed%20in%20the%20limelight%2C%20even%20as%20fellow%20Union%20minister%20Narendra%20Singh%20Tomar%20sat%20sulking.%20The%20occasion%20was%20the%20125th%C2%A0anniversary%20celebration%20of%20The%20Scindia%20School%20in%20Gwalior%20with%20Modi%20in%20attendance.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20picture%20became%20clearer%20soon%20after%20the%20prime%20minister%20exited%20Gwalior%20in%20the%20evening%2C%20as%20the%20fifth%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20list%20of%20candidates%20was%20announced.%20At%20least%20six%20of%20Scindia%20loyalists%2C%20who%20had%20joined%20the%20BJP%20along%20with%20him%20in%202020%20after%20breaking%20away%20from%20the%20Congress%20and%20bringing%20down%20the%20Kamal%20Nath%20government%2C%20were%20denied%20tickets.%20Munnalal%20Goel%20was%20one%20of%20those%20who%20lost%20out%20from%20Gwalior%20East.%20The%20ticket%20went%20to%20ex%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Maya%20Singh%2C%20a%20distant%20aunt%20of%20Scindia%E2%80%99s.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20October%2022%2C%20loyalist-turned-rebel%20Goel%20gheraoed%20the%20Jai%20Vilas%20Palace%20of%20the%20Scindias%20along%20with%20his%20supporters.%20He%20even%20lay%20down%20on%20the%20road%20in%20front%20of%20Scindia%E2%80%99s%20car.%20As%20visuals%20went%20viral%2C%20Scindia%20had%20to%20step%20out%20of%20his%20car%20and%20bodily%20pick%20up%20Goel.%20In%20placatory%20tones%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CEvery%20time%20decisions%20are%20not%20taken%20depending%20on%20what%20we%20want.%20But%20I%20have%20got%20a%20ticket%20for%20Munna%20thrice%20which%20we%20won%20sometime%2C%20lost%20sometime.%20All%20I%20want%20to%20say%20is%20I%20am%20with%20you%20and%20with%20Munna.%E2%80%9D%20No%20one%20looked%20convinced.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20Scindia%20camp%20watch%20their%20boss%E2%80%99s%20clout%20wane%2C%20Scindia%20himself%20would%20have%20thanked%20his%20stars%20that%20he%20had%20not%20been%20named%20in%20the%20fifth%20list.%20Had%20he%20been%20asked%20to%20contest%20from%20Shivpuri%2C%20vacated%20by%20his%20aunt%20Yashodhara%2C%20he%20would%20have%20had%20to%20face%20K.P.%20Singh%2C%20MLA%20for%2030%20years%20from%20the%20Picchore%20seat%20who%20was%20announced%20by%20the%20Congress%20in%20its%20first%20list.%20While%20Singh%20faces%20some%20anti-incumbency%20and%20narrowly%20won%20his%20seat%20in%202018%2C%20he%20is%20nevertheless%20a%20force%20to%20reckon%20with.%20Losing%20to%20Singh%20would%20have%20left%20Scindia%E2%80%99s%20already%20shaky%20reputation%20in%20tatters.%20Earlier%2C%20there%20were%20reports%20that%20Scindia%20could%20be%20fielded%20from%20Gwalior%2C%20a%20family%20bastion%20which%20has%20returned%20three%20generations%20of%20the%20Scindias%2C%20including%20in%20the%202014%20Modi%20wave.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20now%2C%20where%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20rubber%20stamps%20go%2C%20he%20is%20the%20tallest%2C%20far%20ahead%20of%20a%20Manohar%20Lal%20Khattar%20or%20a%20Pushkar%20Dhami.%20The%20BJP%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20really%20done%20anything%20for%20his%20reputation.%20In%20the%20Gwalior%20Chambal%20belt%2C%20his%20once%20stronghold%2C%20he%20is%20seen%20as%20the%20%3Cem%3Egaddar%3C%2Fem%3E%20who%20faces%20greater%20anti-incumbency%20than%20even%20chief%20minister%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan.%20From%20Maharaj%2C%20he%E2%80%99s%20now%20become%20a%20%3Cem%3Ebhaisahab%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20losing%20the%202019%20election%20from%20Guna%20to%20a%20party%20worker.%20His%20legacy%20and%20aura%20completely%20shredded%2C%20he%20is%20now%20seen%20to%20be%20%C2%A0bowing%20and%20scraping%20before%20the%20BJP%20top%20leadership.%20He%E2%80%99s%20pushing%20his%20son%20into%20cricket%20now%2C%20hoping%20to%20draw%20closer%20to%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20through%20his%20son%2C%20BCCI%20president%20Jay%20Shah.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20it%20is%20said%20there%20are%20three%20BJPs%3A%20Shivraj%2C%20Maharaj%20and%20%3Cem%3Enaraz%3C%2Fem%3E%20(upset).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22MP%3A%20Why%20Congress's%20Three%20Promises%20to%20Tribals%20Could%20Be%20a%20Game%20Changer%20in%2047%20ST%20Reserved%20Seats%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmp-why-congresss-three-promises-to-tribals-could-be-a-game-changer-in-47-st-reserved-seats%5C%22%3EMP%3A%20Why%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20Three%20Promises%20to%20Tribals%20Could%20Be%20a%20Game%20Changer%20in%2047%20ST%20Reserved%20Seats%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20Maharaj%20camp%20is%20seeing%20its%20political%20graph%20fall%20and%20fall%2C%20it%20is%20the%20naraz%20camp%20that%20the%20BJP%20top%20leadership%20is%20watching%20with%20growing%20unease.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FSevadalKL%2Fstatus%2F1715769332092014967%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3EDesh%20ke%20gaddaron%3C%2Fa%3E%20ko%2C%20goli%20maaro%20saa*%23%26amp%3B%20ko%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20is%20not%20a%20slogan%20the%20leadership%20in%20Delhi%20thought%20they%20would%20ever%20hear%20being%20directed%20at%20them.%20Add%20to%20that%20October%2021%E2%80%99s%20visuals%20going%20viral%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fnation%2F2023%2Foct%2F23%2Fmp-polls-resentment-overbjp-congress-listsbhupendra-yadav-heckled-by-irate-workers-2626453.html%5C%22%3Eparty%20workers%20heckling%20Union%20minister%20Bhupendra%20Yadav%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20the%20message%20that%20has%20gone%20out%20is%20that%20party%20workers%20have%20lost%20their%20awe%20and%20fear%20of%20the%20twosome%2C%20Modi%20and%20Shah.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNever%20has%20this%20kind%20of%20rebellion%20been%20witnessed%20in%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20prides%20itself%20for%20being%20a%20disciplined%2C%20cadre-based%20organisation.%20This%20is%20a%20sure%20shot%20indication%20that%20the%20Central%20leadership%20has%20lost%20its%20grip%20on%20the%20states.%20There%20are%20too%20many%20rebels%20and%20the%20situation%20is%20akin%20to%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20where%2C%20despite%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20intervention%2C%20the%20rebels%20refused%20to%20budge.%20Another%20reason%20for%20the%20rebellion%20is%20the%20cadre%20is%20telling%20their%20bosses%20that%20they%20cannot%20impose%20their%20will%20on%20the%20organisation.%20Modi%2C%20as%20of%20now%2C%20has%20placed%20rubber%20stamps%20across%20the%20party%20while%20in%20the%20past%20the%20local%20leadership%20decided%20who%20would%20be%20projected.%20The%20rebellion%20is%20to%20send%20the%20message%20that%20Modi%20can%E2%80%99t%20impose%20a%20Congress%20culture%20in%20the%20BJP%2C%E2%80%9D%20political%20commentator%20Ashok%20Wankhede%20says.%20The%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20tagline%2C%20%E2%80%98party%20with%20a%20difference%E2%80%99%2C%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20seem%20have%20takers%20any%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20597px)%2085vw%2C%20597px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F25095958%2FF9BUG9zboAA6VnL.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22597%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F25095958%2FF9BUG9zboAA6VnL.jpeg%20597w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F25095958%2FF9BUG9zboAA6VnL-300x258.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681583%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22513%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EJyotiraditya%20Scindia%20with%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40JM_Scindia%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EActually%2C%20the%20knives%20were%20out%20much%20before%2C%20right%20after%20the%20mayoral%20polls%20in%20July%20last%20year%20when%20the%20BJP%20retained%20only%20nine%20out%20of%2016%20seats%20in%20its%20worst%20performance%20in%20two%20decades.%20It%20lost%2C%20amongst%20others%2C%20its%20stronghold%20of%20Morena%2C%20which%20is%20the%20parliamentary%20constituency%20of%20Union%20minister%20Narendra%20Tomar%20and%20home%20district%20of%20state%20BJP%20president%20V.D.%20Sharma%2C%20in%20a%20stunning%20defeat.%20Though%20the%20party%20won%20a%20majority%20of%20the%20corporation%20elections%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20had%20the%20central%20leadership%20worried.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhich%20is%20why%20when%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Felections%2Fmadhya-pradesh-elections%2Fmadhya-pradesh-election-2023-amit-shah-bjp-will-decide-cm-face-after-mp-election-result-123082100240_1.html%5C%22%3Ea%20non-committal%3C%2Fa%3E%20Amit%20Shah%20said%20the%20party%20will%20decide%20who%20will%20be%20chief%20minister%2C%20and%20that%20the%20election%20would%20be%20fought%20in%20the%20name%20of%20Modi%2C%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-mp-chouhan-s-cm-question-at-rally-creates-unease-in-bjp-101696705272999.html%5C%22%3Erealised%20it%20is%20time%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20do%20his%20own%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fshould-i-become-madhya-pradesh-cm-again-or-not-shivraj-singh-chouhan-asks-people-at-rally%2Farticle67392102.ece%5C%22%3Ebranding%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%20show%20the%20Centre%20who%20is%20boss%2C%20at%20least%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20even%20fielded%20seven%20MPs%2C%20including%20three%20Union%20ministers%2C%20most%20of%20whom%20were%20projecting%20themselves%20as%20a%20CM%20candidate.%20Kailash%20Vijayvargia%20openly%20said%20he%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20contest.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Union%20ministers%20and%20MPs%20were%20fielded%20in%20the%20hope%20that%20rebellion%20would%20be%20stemmed.%20Modi%20is%20no%20longer%20confident%20that%20his%20face%20alone%20is%20good%20enough%20to%20get%20votes.%20In%20the%20past%2C%20it%20was%20said%20Modi%20could%20even%20get%20a%20lamp%20post%20elected.%20Now%20Modi%20is%20asking%20for%20votes%20in%20name%20kamal%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestatesman.com%2Findia%2Flotus-is-our-face-in-this-election-pm-modi-clarifies-in-rajasthan-1503227553.html%5C%22%3Ewell%20like%20in%20Rajasthan%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20indicates%20he%20has%20reached%20saturation%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20political%20watcher%20Nilanjan%20Mukhopadhyay.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20fourth%20list%20it%20became%20clear%20that%20Chouhan%20loyalists%20would%20have%20to%20be%20accommodated%20if%20rebellion%20was%20to%20be%20stemmed.%20For%20the%20first%20time%20perhaps%2C%20the%20Centre%20blinked%20and%20bent%20before%20Chouhan.%20Out%20of%2057%20names%2C%20a%20majority%20were%20those%20that%20Shivraj%20had%20recommended.%20The%20top%20leadership%20nevertheless%20tried%20to%20send%20the%20message%20that%20they%20had%20the%20upper%20hand.%20The%20income%20tax%20surveys%20on%20the%20Trident%20group%2C%20with%20its%20offices%20in%20Budhni%2C%20the%20constituency%20of%20Shivraj%20Chouhan%2C%20is%20being%20seen%20by%20political%20watchers%20as%20an%20indirect%20hit%20against%20the%20chief%20minister.%20The%20yarn%20and%20textile%20major%20is%20said%20to%20be%20close%20to%20Chouhan%2C%20with%20the%20Congress%20often%20alleging%20that%20Chouhan%20is%20a%20co-promoter.%20Ex%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20chief%20secretary%20Anthony%20D%E2%80%99%20Sa%2C%20said%20to%20be%20close%20to%20Chouhan%2C%20is%20on%20the%20Trident%20board.%20The%20simultaneous%20surveys%20were%20in%20Barnala%2C%20Dhaula%2C%20Ludhiana%20in%20Punjab%20and%20elsewhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20there%20are%20plenty%20of%20ticket%20seekers%2C%20how%20many%20are%20winnable%20candidates%20and%20to%20what%20extent%20ideology%20can%20be%20compromised%20was%20apparent%20in%20the%20third%20list%2C%20which%20had%20just%20one%20name%2C%20from%20Chhindwara.%20Monika%20Batti%2C%20the%20candidate%20from%20the%20tribal-dominated%20constituency%20of%20Amarwara%20in%20Chindwara%20district%2C%20is%20the%20daughter%20of%20the%20founder%20of%20the%20Gondwana%20Gantantra%20Party%20and%20ex%20MLA%2C%20the%20late%20Manmohan%20Shah%20Batti.%20She%20joined%20the%20BJP%20a%20week%20before%20her%20name%20was%20announced.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22'Maharaj%20Doesn't%20Have%20Power%20in%20the%20BJP'%3A%20Scindia's%20Clout%20Wanes%20as%20Loyalists%20Return%20to%20Congress%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmaharaj-doesnt-have-power-in-the-bjp-scindias-clout-wanes-as-loyalists-return-to-congress%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Maharaj%20Doesn%E2%80%99t%20Have%20Power%20in%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99%3A%20Scindia%E2%80%99s%20Clout%20Wanes%20as%20Loyalists%20Return%20to%20Congress%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBatti%20is%20an%20unlikely%20choice%20for%20the%20BJP.%20Her%20late%20father%E2%80%99s%20politics%20were%20viewed%20always%20as%20anti-sanatan.%20He%20has%20an%20FIR%20registered%20against%20him%20for%20burning%20the%20Ramayana%20and%20distributing%20%E2%80%98anti-Hindu%E2%80%99%20literature.%20Batti%20senior%20has%20constructed%20a%20temple%20for%20Ravana%20in%20his%20village%2C%20Devri.%20On%20Dusshera%2C%20Devri%20is%20one%20village%20where%20Ravana%E2%80%99s%20effigy%20is%20never%20burnt.%20The%20GGP%2C%20seen%20more%20as%20a%20vote%20cutter%2C%20wears%20its%20anti-Hinduism%20and%20anti-Hindutva%20politics%20on%20its%20sleeve%20and%20advocates%20the%20cause%20of%20Adivasis.%20While%20Monika%20now%20tries%20to%20put%20the%20Ramayana%20burning%20episode%20behind%20her%2C%20she%20does%20admit%20that%20tribals%20pray%20to%20Ravana.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20Centre%20scouted%20for%20winnable%20candidates%2C%20it%20is%20the%20third%20factor%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Shivraj%2C%20who%20is%20watching%20from%20the%20sidelines%2C%20smug%20in%20the%20knowledge%20that%20if%20he%20goes%20down%2C%20so%20will%20his%20opponents%2C%20the%20dozen-odd%20chief%20ministerial%20candidates%20who%20had%20been%20baying%20for%20him%20till%20the%20Central%20leadership%20asked%20them%20to%20contest.%20It%20is%20alleged%20that%20with%20the%20blessings%20of%20the%20RSS%2C%20Shivraj%20not%20long%20ago%20met%20Modi%20and%20gave%20a%20suggestion.%20Either%20he%20should%20be%20asked%20to%20go%20or%20if%20he%20stays%2C%20he%20should%20get%20full%20control%20of%20the%20state%20and%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20top%20leaders%20of%20the%20state%20should%20prove%20their%20worth%20by%20contesting%20elections.%20It%20was%20an%20idea%20that%20clicked%20with%20Modi%2C%20as%20it%20would%20give%20him%20an%20idea%20of%20who%20stood%20where%20ahead%20of%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENow%20stalwarts%20like%20Kailash%20Vijayvargiya%2C%20Union%20ministers%20Narendra%20Tomar%2C%20Faggan%20Singh%20Kulaste%20and%20Prahlad%20Patel%20are%20instead%20of%20baiting%20Chouhan%2C%20busy%20fighting%20to%20protect%20their%20turf.%20Vijayvarghia%20had%20in%20fact%20said%20openly%20he%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fpolitics%2Fmp-polls-not-even-1-wish-to-contest-but-will-follow-party-orders-says-bjps-kailash-vijayvargiya-11695809986022.html%5C%22%3Eno%20wish%20to%20contest%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20too%20is%20playing%20along.%20TV%20actor%20Vikram%20Mastal%2C%20who%20is%20seen%20in%20the%20role%20of%20Hanuman%2C%20has%20been%20fielded%20from%20Budhni.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20calculation%20is%20Shivraj%20should%20win%20by%20a%20huge%20margin%20but%20the%20party%20should%20lose%20so%20the%20message%20goes%20out%20that%20the%20Central%20leadership%20of%20the%20BJP%20is%20responsible%20for%20this%20mess%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Wankhede.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESenior%20to%20Modi%20in%20politics%2C%20Shivraj%20is%20one%20of%20the%20tallest%20OBC%20faces%20in%20the%20party%2C%20credited%20with%20turning%20around%20a%20BIMARU%20state.%20His%20politics%20is%20the%20politics%20of%20Kushabhau%20Thakre%2C%20of%20social%20engineering%2C%20and%20not%20the%20easy%20Hindutva%20of%20the%20Modi-Shah%20duo%20although%20he%20did%20try%20the%20bulldozer%20and%20love%20jihad%20variety%20of%20politics%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20in%20his%20last%20term.%20After%2020%20years%20in%20the%20business%2C%20he%20knows%20the%20stakes%20are%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESays%20journalist%20Sanjeev%20Acharya%2C%20%E2%80%9CShivraj%20is%20doing%20what%20Digvijay%20did%20to%20the%20state%20leadership%20after%20a%20two-year%20term%20when%20he%20lost%20out%20to%20Uma%20Bharati.%20Digvijay%20then%20finished%20off%20the%20state%20Congress%20leadership%20as%20he%20waited%20for%20his%2010%20year%20self-imposed%20to%20exile%20to%20get%20over.%E2%80%9D%20(Congress%20leader%20Digvijay%20Singh%20had%20announced%20in%20the%20assembly%20that%20if%20did%20not%20win%2C%20he%20would%20not%20contest%20any%20election%20for%20the%20next%2010%20years.)%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENow%20Shivraj%20is%20preparing%20for%20a%20very%20long%20haul%2C%20and%20hoping%20he%E2%80%99s%20the%20only%20one%20in%20the%20race%20when%20he%20breasts%20the%20tape.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698215407000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F26210023%2FF6uAo6VbgAAYzDa.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmadhya-pradesh-bjp-shivraj-singh-chouhan-centre%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20it%20is%20said%20there%20are%20three%20BJPs%3A%20Shivraj%2C%20Maharaj%20and%20naraz%20(upset).%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmadhya-pradesh-bjp-shivraj-singh-chouhan-centre%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ananya%20Pandey%20gives%20festive%20fashion%20goals%20in%20exquisite%20lehenga%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698215400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104674648%2Cimgsize-128644.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fweb-stories%2Fananya-pandey-gives-festive-fashion-goals-in-exquisite-lehenga%2Fphotostory%2F104674648.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F104674648.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EAnanya%20Pandey%20turned%20heads!%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fweb-stories%2Fananya-pandey-gives-festive-fashion-goals-in-exquisite-lehenga%2Fphotostory%2F104674648.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20new%20bill%20in%20Congress%20is%20going%20to%20'kill'%20card%20rewards%20programs%2C%20says%20United%20CEO%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Scott%20Kirby%20thinks%20lower%20revenues%20for%20Visa%20and%20Mastercard%20will%20make%20them%20pull%20out%20of%20rewards%20programs.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6538aef90487ff031cad8c9c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EScott%20Kirby%20thinks%20lower%20revenues%20for%20Visa%20and%20Mastercard%20will%20make%20them%20pull%20out%20of%20rewards%20programs.%3Cp%3EKevin%20Dietsch%2FGetty%20Images%20and%20Nicolas%20Economou%2FNurPhoto%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EUnited%20CEO%20Scott%20Kirby%20says%20a%20new%20bill%20in%20Congress%20is%20putting%20miles%20programs%20on%20the%20chopping%20block.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Credit%20Card%20Competition%20Act%2C%20proposed%20by%20Sen.%20Dick%20Durbin%2C%20seeks%20to%20lower%20card%20swipe%20fees.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20Kirby%20said%20lower%20revenues%20for%20Visa%20and%20Mastercard%20would%20make%20them%20stop%20offering%20reward%20points.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EUnited%20Airlines%20CEO%20Scott%20Kirby%20warned%20last%20week%20that%20airline%20customers%20could%20start%20seeing%20their%20miles%20programs%20disappear%20because%20of%20a%20new%20bipartisan%20congressional%20bill%20on%20credit%20card%20swipe%20fees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20would%20kill%20rewards%20programs%2C%26quot%3B%20United%20CEO%20Scott%20Kirby%20said%20in%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fir.united.com%2Fevents%2Fevent-details%2F3q23-earnings-call%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOctober%2018%20earnings%20call%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BIt%20would%20not%20exist%20anymore.%20It%20will%20kill%20debit%20card%20rewards%20programs%20when%20it%20happens%2C%20and%20I%20think%20it's%20bad%20policy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insiderintelligence.com%2Fcontent%2Fbipartisan-us-bill-expected-take-aim-credit-card-swipe-fees%3FIR%3DT%26itm_source%3Dbusinessinsider%26itm_medium%3Dcontent_marketing%26itm_campaign%3Dbriefing_post%26itm_content%3Dredirect%26itm_term%3Dpayments-innovation%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECredit%20Card%20Competition%20Act%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20proposed%20by%20Sen.%20Dick%20Durbin%20of%20Illinois%2C%20seeks%20to%20end%20what%20Durbin%20calls%20a%20%26quot%3BVisa-Mastercard%20duopoly%26quot%3B%20over%20credit%20card%20transactions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETogether%2C%20Visa%20and%20Mastercard%20control%2080%25%20of%20US%20credit%20card%20payments%2C%20and%20charge%20merchants%20transaction%20fees%20of%20around%202%20to%203%25%2C%20according%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.durbin.senate.gov%2Fimo%2Fmedia%2Fdoc%2FThe%2520Credit%2520Card%2520Competition%2520Act%2520of%25202023%2520-%2520one-pager.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esummary%20of%20the%20bill%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Retailers%20and%20businesses%20tend%20to%20pass%20the%20cost%20of%20those%20swipe%20fees%20on%20to%20their%20customers%2C%20resulting%20in%20higher%20prices%20for%20consumers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDurbin%2C%20a%20Democrat%20lawmaker%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.congress.gov%2Fbill%2F118th-congress%2Fsenate-bill%2F1838%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eintroduced%20the%20bill%20in%20June%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20aims%20to%20require%20big%20US%20banks%20to%20allow%20at%20least%20one%20other%20payment%20network%20besides%20Visa%20or%20Mastercard%20to%20be%20used%20in%20credit%20card%20transactions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20hope%20here%20is%20to%20introduce%20competition%20that%20would%20compel%20the%20payment%20giants%20to%20lower%20their%20fees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bill%20was%20originally%20introduced%20by%20Durbin%20in%20the%20previous%20Congress%20in%202022%2C%20though%20it%20never%20came%20to%20a%20vote.%20Now%2C%20it's%20been%20re-introduced%20with%20growing%20bipartisan%20support%2C%20including%20Republican%20and%20Democrat%20co-sponsors%20in%20the%20Senate%20and%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20several%20airlines%2C%20which%20partner%20with%20banks%20to%20issue%20miles%20or%20loyalty%20reward%20points%2C%20say%20the%20bill%20will%20cut%20Visa%20and%20Mastercard's%20revenues%20and%20make%20them%20less%20willing%20to%20participate%20in%20rewards%20programs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDelta%20Air%20Lines%20CEO%20Ed%20Bastian%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2023-10-24%2Fmajor-airline-ceos-predict-loyalty-program-doom-under-proposal%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20he%20predicted%20banks%20would%20stop%20such%20partnerships%20if%20the%20bill%20passed%2C%20resulting%20in%20%26quot%3Bunbelievable%26quot%3B%20consumer%20backlash.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20cards%20could%20no%20longer%20receive%20the%20funding%20to%20be%20able%20to%20invest%20in%20rewards-back%20opportunities.%20It's%20something%20that%20we're%20watching%2C%20obviously%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20outlet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20United%20earnings%20call%2C%20Kirby%20criticized%20Durbin's%20bill%2C%20saying%20the%20vast%20majority%20of%20US%20consumers%20are%20on%20at%20least%20one%20rewards%20program.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAlmost%20everyone%20has%20one%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20they%20like%20them%20a%20lot.%20Our%20customers%20certainly%20like%20them%20a%20lot.%20And%20so%20I%20think%20it'd%20be%20hard%20in%20Congress%20to%20take%20a%20vote%20that%2084%25%20of%20your%20voters%20are%20going%20to%20be%20upset%20with%20the%20outcome%20of%20that%20vote.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20death%20of%20loyalty%20programs%20would%20also%20cut%20deep%20into%20airlines'%20profits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20carriers%20that%20partner%20with%20credit%20cards%20to%20offer%20points%20or%20miles%20programs%20often%20get%20paid%20each%20time%20a%20customer%20uses%20these%20cards%2C%20generating%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffinance.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2Funited-airlines-loyalty-program-worth-203057453.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebillions%20in%20revenue%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20supporters%20of%20the%20Credit%20Card%20Competition%20Act%20say%20it%20will%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmerchantspaymentscoalition.com%2Fnew-estimate-shows-credit-card-competition-act-would-save-merchants-and-consumers-15-billion-a-year%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecreate%20%2415%20billion%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20savings%20for%20retailers%2C%20restaurants%2C%20small%20businesses%2C%20and%20their%20customers%20every%20year.%20They%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnrf.com%2Fblog%2F4-things-know-about-credit-card-competition-act%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eargue%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20big%20banks%20will%20continue%20to%20offer%20reward%20programs%20after%20the%20bill%20is%20passed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%20European%20Union%20already%20places%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-eu-antitrust-payment-idUSKBN240293%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehard%20cap%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20credit%20card%20transaction%20fees%20at%200.3%25.%20European%20banks%20and%20airlines%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.miles-and-more.com%2Frow%2Fen%2Fprogram%2Fnews%2Fdeutsche-bank-mastercard-news-2023.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estill%20offer%3C%2Fa%3E%20points%20and%20miles%20programs%20to%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDurbin%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20sent%20outside%20regular%20business%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcongress-billcredit-card-fees-kill-flier-miles-united-scott-kirby-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698215286000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6538aef90487ff031cad8c9c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcongress-billcredit-card-fees-kill-flier-miles-united-scott-kirby-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BThis%20would%20kill%20rewards%20programs%2C%26quot%3B%20Kirby%20said%20in%20an%20earnings%20call.%20%26quot%3BIt%20would%20not%20exist%20anymore.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mloh%40insider.com%20(Matthew%20Loh)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcongress-billcredit-card-fees-kill-flier-miles-united-scott-kirby-2023-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Fidias%3A%20YouTuber%20sorry%20for%20freeloading%20stunt%20video%20in%20Japan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698214863000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2FA552%2Fproduction%2F_131522324_fidias2.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-67213167%22