rgency%20shelters%20and%20away%20from%20rivers%2C%20streams%20and%20ravines.%20Hurricanes%20hit%20Mexico%20every%20year%20on%20both%20its%20Pacific%20and%20Atlantic%20coasts%2C%20usually%20between%20May%20and%20November%2C%20though%20few%20make%20landfall%20as%20a%20Category%205.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fpotentially-catastrophic-hurricane-otis-heads-for-mexico%2Farticleshow%2F104686307.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fpotentially-catastrophic-hurricane-otis-heads-for-mexico%2Famp_articleshow%2F104686307.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fpotentially-catastrophic-hurricane-otis-heads-for-mexico%2Famp_articleshow%2F104686307.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bill%20Gates%20Flew%20Economy%20For%20Years%2C%20Reveals%20Netflix%20Co-Founder.%20Here's%20Why%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%20Founder%20Bill%20Gates%2C%20the%20ninth%20richest%20man%20in%20the%20world%2C%20used%20to%20fly%20economy%20class%20on%20flights%20for%20many%20years.%20This%20was%20revealed%20by%20the%20Co-founder%20of%20Netflix%2C%20Marc%20Randolph.%20He%20also%20shared%20an%20interesting%20reason%20for%20the%20same%20and%20stated%20that%20Mr%20Gates%20did%20not%20consider%20flying%20by%20first%20class%20to%20be%20of%20%26quot%3Bgood%20value%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Randolph%20took%20to%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter%20and%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BFor%20many%20years%2C%20Bill%20Gates%20used%20to%20fly%20Economy%2C%20not%20because%20he%20couldn't%20afford%20First%20Class%2C%20but%20because%20he%20didn't%20consider%20it%20good%20value.%20It's%20five%20or%20six%20times%20more%20expensive%2C%20but%20only%20marginally%20better%20(and%20you%20all%20get%20to%20your%20destination%20at%20the%20same%20time).%26quot%3B%20He%20also%20shared%20a%20picture%20of%20the%20billionaire%20working%20on%20his%20laptop%20while%20sitting%20in%20the%20economy%20section%20of%20an%20aircraft.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EFor%20many%20years%2C%20Bill%20Gates%20used%20to%20fly%20Economy%2C%20not%20because%20he%20couldn't%20afford%20First%20Class%2C%20but%20because%20he%20didn't%20consider%20it%20good%20value.%20It's%20five%20or%20six%20times%20more%20expensive%2C%20but%20only%20marginally%20better%20(and%20you%20all%20get%20to%20your%20destination%20at%20the%20same%20time).%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cbr%3E%20In%20the%20same%20vein%2C%20I%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FCm8HgKlqTS%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FCm8HgKlqTS%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%E2%80%94%20Marc%20Randolph%20(%40mbrandolph)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmbrandolph%2Fstatus%2F1716197513559228692%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%2022%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%20%3Cp%3EHe%20then%20drew%20a%20parallel%20and%20said%20that%20even%20though%20he%20can%20afford%20a%20luxury%20car%2C%20he%20does%20not%20intend%20to%20buy%20it%20because%20his%20Volvo%20station%20wagon%20%26quot%3Bdoes%20the%20job%20just%20fine%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BIn%20the%20same%20vein%2C%20I%20could%20afford%20a%20really%20nice%20car%20at%20this%20point%2C%20but%20I've%20never%20been%20a%20car%20guy%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20need%20a%20Lamborghini%20or%20a%20Mazerati%20(which%20I%20can't%20even%20spell).%20A%20Volvo%20station%20wagon%20does%20the%20job%20just%20fine%2C%20and%20I%20wouldn't%20value%20the%20difference.%20I%20don't%20need%20to%20drop%20%241000%20on%20a%20bottle%20of%20wine%20at%20dinner%20either%2C%20since%20I%20know%20I'll%20get%20the%20same%20enjoyment%20from%20a%20%2435%20bottle%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued%20on%20the%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Netflix%20Co-founder%20then%20stated%20that%20having%20enough%20money%20brings%20both%20security%20and%20freedom.%20%26quot%3BSo%20what%20is%20wealth%20good%20for%2C%20in%20the%20end%3F%20Besides%20providing%20security%2C%20it%20also%20gives%20flexibility.%20After%20all%20of%20the%20experiences%20I've%20had%2C%20the%20most%20important%20thing%20I've%20learned%20about%20money%20is%20that%2C%20once%20you%20have%20enough%20(by%20the%20previous%20definition)%2C%20you%20can%20choose%20to%20have%20less%20of%20it%20in%20exchange%20for%20choosing%20how%20to%20spend%20your%20time.%20And%20spending%20your%20time%20doing%20something%20meaningful%20to%20you...that's%20worth%20way%20more%20than%20a%20Mazerati%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20concluded.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESince%20being%20shared%2C%20his%20post%20has%20amassed%203.9%20million%20views%20and%20over%2013%2C000%20likes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20user%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWealth%20for%20me%20is%20the%20opportunity%20to%20invest%20in%20founders%20and%20startups%20that%20I%20want%20to%20see%20win%20because%20they%20aspire%20to%20solve%20problems%20that%20I%20care%20about%20deeply.%26quot%3B%20Replying%20to%20him%2C%20Mr%20Randolph%20said%20that%20he%20could%20%26quot%3Brelate%20to%20that%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMoney%20buys%20you%20time%2C%20freedom%20and%20flexibility%2C%20that%20is%20what%20really%20makes%20me%20feel%20'rich'%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20another%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnother%20commented%2C%20%26quot%3BPerfectly%20stated.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20some%20people%20had%20a%20different%20outlook%20on%20Mr%20Randolph's%20post.%20%26quot%3BA%20couple%20of%20notes%3A%20-%20when%20he%20was%20flying%20economy%2C%20the%20seats%20were%20probably%20the%20size%20of%20current%20%26quot%3Bpremium%20economy%26quot%3B.%20-%20when%20you%20go%20above%20a%20certain%20level%2Fprice%20you%20need%20to%20be%20able%20to%20appreciate%20the%20quality%20otherwise%20everything%20looks%20the%20same.%20This%20is%20true%20for%20both%20cars%20and%20wine%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20user%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFlying%20economy%20despite%20affording%20better%20isn't%20a%20flex.%20Your%20legs%20deserve%20to%20not%20swell%20if%20you%20can%20afford%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20another%20user.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20third%20person%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BBill%20Gates%20only%20flew%20economy%20because%20Microsoft%20made%20everyone%20in%20the%20company%20fly%20economy%2C%20probably%20due%20to%20Gates%20trying%20to%20save%20a%20buck.%20And%20he%20bought%20a%20private%20jet%20in%201997.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698205740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-02%2F28nkia78_bill-gates-reuters_625x300_10_February_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbill-gates-flew-economy-for-years-reveals-netflix-co-founder-heres-why-4511071%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22He%20also%20shared%20a%20picture%20of%20the%20Bill%20Gates%20working%20on%20his%20laptop%20while%20sitting%20in%20the%20economy%20section%20of%20an%20aircraft.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A25%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbill-gates-flew-economy-for-years-reveals-netflix-co-founder-heres-why-4511071%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbill-gates-flew-economy-for-years-reveals-netflix-co-founder-heres-why-4511071%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbill-gates-flew-economy-for-years-reveals-netflix-co-founder-heres-why-4511071%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tata-owned%20Air%20India%20Express%20to%20double%20its%20pilot%20count%20in%20next%20one%20year%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698205548000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-03%2F27%2Ffull%2F1679927845-8786.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Ftata-owned-air-india-expres