re-real-estate-crisis-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hui%20Ka%20Yan%20is%20now%20worth%20%24979%20million.%20His%20net%20worth%20has%20taken%20a%2098%25%20tumble%20since%20peaking%20at%20%2442%20billion%20in%202017%2C%20per%20Bloomberg.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22htan%40insider.com%20(Huileng%20Tan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A175%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-evergrande-founder-no-longer-billionaire-real-estate-crisis-2023-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BUnlawful%2C%20Unjustifiable%26quot%3B%3A%20Antony%20Blinken%20Compares%20Hamas%20To%2026%2F11%20Terrorists%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUS%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Antony%20Blinken%20has%20drawn%20a%20parallel%20between%20the%20terrorist%20attacks%20by%20Lashkar-e-Taiba%20in%20Mumbai%20and%20Hamas%20in%20Israel%2C%20emphasising%20that%20all%20acts%20of%20terrorism%20are%20%26quot%3Bunlawful%20and%20unjustifiable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20the%20United%20States%20Security%20Council%20ministerial%20meeting%20regarding%20the%20situation%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20following%20the%20October%207%20attack%20on%20Israel%20by%20Gaza-based%20Hamas%2C%20Blinken%20denounced%20member%20states%20that%20provide%20support%2C%20including%20arming%2C%20funding%2C%20and%20training%2C%20to%20terrorist%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20must%20affirm%20the%20right%20of%20any%20nation%20to%20defend%20itself%20and%20to%20prevent%20such%20horror%20from%20repeating%20itself.%20No%20member%20of%20this%20Council%2C%20no%20nation%20in%20this%20entire%20body%20could%20or%20would%20tolerate%20the%20slaughter%20of%20its%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20US%20Secretary%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20statement%2C%20Blinken%20highlighted%20similarities%20between%20terrorist%20attacks%20perpetrated%20by%20Hamas%20against%20Israel%20and%20those%20by%20the%20Pakistan-based%20terror%20organization%20Lashkar-e-Taiba%20in%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20this%20Council%20and%20the%20UN%20General%20Assembly%20have%20repeatedly%20affirmed%2C%20all%20acts%20of%20terrorism%20are%20unlawful%20and%20unjustifiable.%20They're%20unlawful%20and%20unjustifiable%2C%20whether%20they%20target%20people%20in%20Nairobi%20or%20Bali%20Istanbul%20or%20Mumbai%2C%20in%20New%20York%20or%20Kibbutz%20Be'eri%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20are%20unlawful%20and%20unjustifiable%20whether%20they're%20carried%20out%20by%20ISIS%2C%20by%20Boko%20Haram%2C%20by%20Al%20Shabaab%2C%20by%20Lashkar-e-Taiba%20or%20by%20Hamas.%20They%20are%20unlawful%20and%20unjustifiable%20whether%20victims%20are%20targeted%20for%20their%20faith%2C%20their%20ethnicity%2C%20their%20nationality%20or%20any%20other%20reason%2C%26quot%3B%20Blinken%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20emphasised%20the%20Security%20Council's%20responsibility%20to%20condemn%20member%20states%20that%20provide%20support%20in%20terms%20of%20arming%2C%20financing%2C%20and%20training%20to%20Hamas%20or%20any%20other%20terrorist%20group%20involved%20in%20such%20heinous%20acts.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBlinken's%20comments%20were%20in%20reference%20to%20the%2026%2F11%20Mumbai%20terror%20attacks%20carried%20out%20by%20the%20Pakistan-based%20terrorist%20organisation%20Lashkar-e-Taiba.%20These%20attacks%2C%20which%20occurred%20in%202008%2C%20resulted%20in%20the%20tragic%20loss%20of%20166%20lives%2C%20including%20six%20Americans.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20attacks%2C%20ten%20Pakistani%20terrorists%20laid%20siege%20to%20Mumbai%20for%20over%2060%20hours%2C%20targeting%20and%20killing%20individuals%20in%20India's%20financial%20hub.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBlinken%20also%20said%20%26quot%3Bhumanitarian%20pauses%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20Gaza%20war%20must%20be%20considered%20in%20order%20to%20protect%20Palestinian%20civilians%2C%20The%20Times%20of%20Israel%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBlinken's%20idea%20falls%20short%20of%20a%20ceasefire%20which%20US%20officials%20have%20rejected%20in%20recent%20days%20as%20a%20step%20that%20would%20amount%20to%20help%20for%20Hamas%2C%20arguing%20that%20Israel%20still%20has%20a%20right%20to%20forcefully%20respond%20to%20the%20October%207%20onslaught%20in%20order%20to%20ensure%20that%20it%20doesn't%20happen%20again%2C%20according%20to%20The%20Times%20of%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPalestinian%20civilians%20must%20be%20protected.%20That%20means%20Hamas%20must%20cease%20using%20them%20as%20human%20shields.%20It's%20hard%20to%20think%20of%20an%20act%20of%20greater%20cynicism%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20means%20Israel%20must%20take%20all%20possible%20precautions%20to%20avoid%20harm%20to%20civilians.%20It%20means%20food%2C%20water%2C%20medicine%20and%20other%20essential%20humanitarian%20assistance%20must%20be%20able%20to%20flow%20into%20Gaza%20and%20to%20the%20people%20who%20need%20it.%20It%20means%20civilians%20must%20be%20able%20to%20get%20out%20of%20harm's%20way.%20It%20means%20humanitarian%20pauses%20must%20be%20considered%20for%20these%20purposes%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20US%20State%20Secretary%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20official%20also%20called%20out%20the%20international%20community%20for%20failing%20to%20explicitly%20condemn%20the%20October%207%20Hamas%20onslaught.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20in%20his%20speech%20he%20said%20that%20in%20his%20conversations%20with%20world%20leaders%20since%20the%20assault%2C%20there%20has%20been%20agreement%20that%20countries%20have%20a%20right%20and%20obligation%20to%20respond%20to%20terror%20attacks%20against%20their%20civilians%20but%20indicates%20that%20not%20all%20of%20them%20have%20acknowledged%20this%20publicly.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Israel%20has%20demanded%20the%20resignation%20of%20United%20Nations%20Secretary-General%20Antonio%20Guterres%20from%20his%20position%20over%20his%20remarks%20against%20the%20Israeli%20counteroffensive%20in%20Gaza%20after%20terror%20attacks%20by%20Hamas%20on%20October%207.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20envoy%20to%20the%20UN%2C%20Gilad%20Erdan%20called%20Guterres%20%26quot%3Bunfit%26quot%3B%20to%20lead%20the%20UN%20and%20called%20for%20his%20resignation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20came%20after%20the%20UN%20chief%20said%20that%20the%20attacks%20by%20Hamas%20%26quot%3Bdid%20not%20happen%20in%20a%20vacuum%26quot%3B%20further%20adding%20that%20the%20attacks%20cannot%20justify%20the%20%26quot%3Bcollective%20punishment%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20people%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20important%20to%20also%20recognize%20the%20attacks%20by%20Hamas%20did%20not%20happen%20in%20a%20vacuum.%20The%20Palestinian%20people%20have%20been%20subjected%20to%2056%20years%20of%20suffocating%20occupation.%20They%20have%20seen%20their%20land%20steadily%20devoured%20by%20settlements%20and%20plagued%20by%20violence%3B%20their%20economy%20stifled%3B%20their%20people%20displaced%20and%20their%20homes%20demolished.%20Their%20hopes%20for%20a%20political%20solution%20to%20their%20plight%20have%20been%20vanishing%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20UN%20chief%20said%20at%20the%20General%20Assembly%26quot%3B%2C%20as%20per%20The%20Times%20of%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Ministry%20of%20Health%20in%20Gaza%20has%20reported%20over%205%2C000%20Palestinians%20have%20been%20killed%20so%20far%2C%20including%20over%202%2C000%20children%20and%201%2C100%20women%20as%20well%20as%20journalists%2C%20medical%20workers%20and%20first%20responders%2C%20with%20more%20than%2015%2C000%20injured.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698205260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-06%2F8h2pd1hg_antony-blinken-_625x300_20_June_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Funlawful-unjustifiable-antony-blinken-