oundtree%2C%20heralded%20as%20%26quot%3Bthe%20first%20Black%20action%20hero%26quot%3B%20for%20his%20starring%20role%20in%20the%20iconic%201971%20hit%20%3Ci%3EShaft%3C%2Fi%3E%2C%20died%20Tuesday%20at%2081%2C%20US%20media%20reported.%20Hollywood%20publication%20Deadline%20said%20that%20the%20actor%2C%20known%20for%20opening%20doors%20for%20other%20Black%20artists%20in%20the%20industry%2C%20died%20with%20his%20family%20at%20his%20bedside%2C%20%26quot%3Bafter%20a%20brief%20battle%20with%20pancreatic%20cancer.%26quot%3B%20%3Ci%3EShaft%3C%2Fi%3E%2C%20in%20which%20Roundtree%20played%20the%20eponymous%20private%20eye%20John%20Shaft%2C%20sparked%20a%20series%20of%20sequels%20and%20a%20TV%20spinoffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFive%20decades%20later%2C%20Roundtree%20was%20still%20acting%2C%20appearing%20in%20the%20television%20romance%20drama%20%3Ci%3ECherish%20the%20Day%3C%2Fi%3E%20and%20film%20comedy%20%3Ci%3EMoving%20On%3C%2Fi%3E%20just%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRichard's%20work%20and%20career%20served%20as%20a%20turning%20point%20for%20African%20American%20leading%20men%20in%20film%2C%26quot%3B%20his%20manager%20Patrick%20McMinn%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20Variety.%20%26quot%3BThe%20impact%20he%20had%20on%20the%20industry%20cannot%20be%20overstated.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERoundtree's%20major%20debut%2C%20%3Ci%3EShaft%3C%2Fi%3E%20was%20hailed%20as%20a%20founding%20classic%20in%20the%20%26quot%3BBlaxploitation%26quot%3B%20genre%20the%201970s%20were%20known%20for%20-%20which%20boosters%20say%20tackled%20race%20relations%20while%20critics%20blast%20the%20style%20for%20trafficking%20in%20stereotypes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEither%20way%2C%20the%20genre%20was%20critical%20to%20pushing%20Hollywood%20to%20finally%20cast%20Black%20Americans%20in%20starring%20roles.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20used%20to%20look%20at%20it%20as%20a%20double-edged%20sword.%20But%20I've%20had%20so%20many%20people%20from%20all%20over%20the%20country%20-%20and%20all%20over%20the%20world%20actually%20-%20come%20up%20and%20say%20what%20that%20film%20meant%20to%20them%20back%20in%20'71%2C%26quot%3B%20Roundtree%20told%20broadcaster%20NPR%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20heavy.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BThe%20other%20side%20of%20it%20is%20I%20got%20typecast%20for%20quite%20some%20time%2C%20and%20then%20I've%20gone%20out%20of%20my%20way%20to%20establish%20a%20different%20side%20of%20my%20acting%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20largely%20successful%20in%20that%20endeavor%2C%20with%20%26quot%3Bhis%20trailblazing%20career%20(changing)%20the%20face%20of%20entertainment%20around%20the%20globe%2C%26quot%3B%20his%20agency%20told%20Deadline.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHis%20enduring%20legacy%20will%20be%20felt%20for%20generations%20to%20come.%20Our%20hearts%20are%20with%20his%20family%20and%20loved%20ones%20during%20this%20difficult%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698203460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fmsplkf98_-richard_625x300_25_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fveteran-actor-richard-roundtree-star-of-shaft-dies-at-81-4511020%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Richard%20Roundtree%20was%20heralded%20as%20%26quot%3Bthe%20first%20Black%20action%20hero%26quot%3B%20for%20his%20role%20in%20the%20iconic%201971%20hit%20Shaft%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fveteran-actor-richard-roundtree-star-of-shaft-dies-at-81-4511020%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fveteran-actor-richard-roundtree-star-of-shaft-dies-at-81-4511020%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertai