inian%2C%20waves%20a%20paper%20carrying%20the%20statistics%20of%20such%20deaths%20over%20a%20decade%20and%20a%20half.%20He%20suggests%20roughly%20about%207%2C000%20Palestinians%20to%20some%20400%20Israelis%20killed%20in%20the%20everyday%20conflict%20caused%20by%20Israeli%20occupation%20of%20Gaza%20and%20West%20Bank%20in%20that%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYoussef%20urges%20the%20world%20to%20tell%20Palestinians%20if%20this%20exchange%20rate%20of%20deaths%20will%20change%20after%20the%20recent%20Hamas%20attack.%20%E2%80%9CPlease%20tell%20us%20what%20the%20new%20exchange%20rate%20is.%20At%20least%20we%20will%20know%20what%20the%20Palestinians%20should%20be%20prepared%20for!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%20of%20the%20Morgan%20show%20last%20week%2C%20Israel%20had%20lost%201%2C400%20to%20the%20Hamas%20attack%20and%20the%20relentless%C2%A0%20bombing%20of%20Gaza%20had%20taken%20a%20toll%20of%203%2C500%20Palestinians.%20The%20Palestinian%20death%20toll%20today%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2F031befba-3370-4046-b8c6-363b3637d966%3Fj%3DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2F031befba-3370-4046-b8c6-363b3637d966%3Fj%253DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1698287481815000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw2rLZxVeJ9J0EU0l0hvJBIs%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estands%20at%20over%206%2C000%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYoussef%E2%80%99s%20rhetorical%20question%20may%20seem%20like%20dark%20humour%20taken%20to%20another%20level%20but%20it%20is%20also%20deeply%20disturbing%C2%A0%20because%20in%20the%20%E2%80%98peace%20diplomacy%E2%80%99%20practiced%20by%20the%20%E2%80%98civilised%E2%80%99%20world%E2%80%99%20(the%20UN%20included)%2C%20such%20proportionality%20of%20punishment%20is%20taken%20very%20seriously%20though%20it%20remains%20formally%20unstated.%20After%20all%2C%20even%20the%20UN%20chief%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2Fc38f10c5-d8af-438e-b57e-2e2b7b51b1f2%3Fj%3DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2Fc38f10c5-d8af-438e-b57e-2e2b7b51b1f2%3Fj%253DeyJ1IjoiaHpuMnUifQ.MQOquijPBw98XVYBc9m195DW7Qx9ruSvngQYE7EwHGg%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1698287481815000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw3L71XcbtO6EqYV0Nqd9RTS%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecalled%20for%20a%20ceasefire%20only%2011%20days%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0after%20the%20Hamas%20attack%20and%20subsequent%20Israeli%20bombing.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%20the%20question%20posed%20by%20Youssef%20is%20a%20serious%20one%20and%20is%20relevant%20even%20today%20as%20the%20Palestinian%20toll%20continues%20to%20rise%20sharply%20and%20Israel%20prepares%20for%20a%20ground%20action.%20The%20ratio%20of%20killings%20for%20over%20a%20decade%20before%20the%20recent%20Hamas%20attack%20was%20roughly%20400%20Israelis%20to%20about%207%2C000%20Palestinians.%20That%20is%20over%2017%20times%20Palestinians%20killed%20in%20the%20conflict%20ostensibly%20during%20peacetime.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EObviously%2C%20this%20ratio%20will%20change%20during%20a%20full%20scale%20war%2C%20as%20is%20happening%20now.%20Therefore%2C%20Youssef%20wants%20to%20know%20what%20is%20the%20new%20exchange%20rate%20that%20Israel%20and%20its%20key%20Western%20allies%20would%20settle%20at.%20The%20key%20question%20is%20after%20how%20many%20Palestinian%20deaths%20will%20the%20American%20establishment%20formally%20call%20for%20a%20ceasefire%3F%20The%20so-called%20peace%20time%20exchange%20rate%20of%20sacrificing%2017%20times%20Palestinian%20lives%20might%20take%20the%20civilian%20toll%20to%20well%20over%2020%2C000%20in%20Gaza%20(1%2C400%20%C3%9717)%20in%20the%20present%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20Israel%20and%20its%20Western%20allies%20will%20not%20go%20that%20far.%20For%20such%20a%20genocidal%20exchange%20rate%20in%20wartime%20could%20trigger%20a%20wider%20conflagration%20in%20West%20Asia.%20As%20Youssef%20says%2C%20the%20colonisers%20at%20some%20point%20will%20stop%20and%20say%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20feel%20sorry%20for%20what%20happened%20to%20you.%E2%80%9D%20They%20did%20it%20to%20the%20native%20Americans%20in%20the%2019th%20century.%20After%20reducing%20their%20population%20to%20less%20than%2010%25%2C%20the%20colonisers%20felt%20sorry%20and%20stopped.%20Modern%20diplomacy%20has%20perhaps%20created%20a%20more%20refined%20version%20of%20such%20proportionality%20between%20the%20colonisers%20and%20the%20colonised.%20Of%20course%2C%20the%20Anglo-Saxon%20world%20has%20had%20enough%20net%20practice%20over%20past%20centuries%20of%20arriving%20at%20such%20an%20exchange%20rate%20of%20killings%20in%20the%20act%20of%20colonisation%20as%20well%20as%20during%20war.%20Sometimes%2C%20it%20is%20not%20even%20necessary%20to%20use%20arms%2C%20ammunition%20and%20bombing%20to%20arrive%20at%20a%20new%20exchange%20rate%20of%20deaths%20during%20war.%20After%20all%20Winston%20Churchill%20achieved%20it%20by%20simply%20diverting%20food%20grains%20from%20Bengal%20to%20the%20warfront%20to%20feed%20British%20soldiers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%20Israel-Palestine%20war%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20real%20peacetime%20since%201948%2C%20when%20%E2%80%93%20under%20the%20aegis%20of%20the%20UN%20%E2%80%93%20the%20territorial%20division%20of%20the%20former%20British%20mandate%20territory%20started%20with%20roughly%2045%25%20for%20Palestine%20and%2055%25%20for%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EToday%20Israel%20hold%2077%25%20of%20the%20land%20and%20even%20in%20the%20remaining%2023%25%2C%20Israeli%20military%20occupation%20persists.%20And%20this%20has%20been%20accompanied%20by%20decades%20of%20a%20constantly%20shifting%20exchange%20rate%20of%20killings%20on%20both%20sides.%20Of%20course%2C%20the%20coloniser%20backed%20by%20the%20mighty%20global%20military-industrial%20complex%20sets%20a%20hugely%20favourable%C2%A0%20exchange%20rate%20with%20ruthless%20efficiency%2C%20notwithstanding%20all%20the%20politically%20correct%20UN%20resolutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYoussef%E2%80%99s%20question%20has%20profound%20implications%20in%20the%20amoral%20world%20of%20diplomacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20piece%20was%20first%20published%20on%20The%20India%20Cable%20%E2%80%93%20a%20premium%20newsletter%20from%20The%20Wire%20%26amp%3B%20Galileo%20Ideas%20%E2%80%93%20and%20has%20been%20republished%20here.%20To%20subscribe%20to%20The%20India%20Cable%2C%20click%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheindiacable.com%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698202905000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F19092706%2FF8t8SUEWMAAvoa0.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fa-satirist-calls-out-the-calculus-of-the-horror-of-war-the-cost-must-count%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20ratio%20of%20killings%20for%20over%20a%20decade%20before%20the%20recent%20Hamas%20attack%20was%20roughly%20400%20Israelis%20to%20about%207%2C000%20Palestinians.%20That%20is%20over%2017%20times%20Palestinians%20killed%20in%20the%20conflict%20ostensibly%20during%20peacetime.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fa-satirist-calls-out-the-calculus-of-the-horror-of-war-the-cost-must-count%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Raytheon's%20CEO%20said%20on%20an%20earnings%20call%20that%20the%20company%20stood%20to%20'benefit'%20from%20DoD%20budget%20increases%20due%20to%20the%20war%20in%20Israel%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Iron%20dome%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65387b070487ff031cad7788%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIsraeli%20Iron%20Dome%20air%20defense%20system%20fires%20to%20intercept%20a%20rocket%20fired%20from%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20in%20Ashkelon%2C%20Israel%2C%20Thursday%2C%20Oct.19%2C%202023.%20Since%20Israel%20activated%20the%20Iron%20Dome%20in%202011%2C%20the%20cutting-edge%20rocket-defense%20system%20has%20intercepted%20thousands%20of%20rockets%20fired%20from%20the%20Gaza%20Strip.%20By%20Israeli%20military%20estimates%2C%20Hamas%20has%20already%20fired%207%2C000%20rockets%20into%20Israel%20during%20the%20current%20war.%3Cp%3E(AP%20Photo%2FTsafrir%20Abayov%2C%20File)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EPresident%20Biden%20requested%20an%20additional%20%24106%20billion%20to%20the%20DoD%20budget%2C%20citing%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20war%20and%20other%20global%20conflicts.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20CEO%20of%20military%20contractor%20RTX%20said%20Tuesday%20the%20company%20could%20%26quot%3Bbenefit%26quot%3B%20from%20an%20increased%20DoD%20budget.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ERTX%20Corporation%2C%20formerly%20known%20as%20Raytheon%2C%20is%20a%20long-time%20US%20defense%20contractor%20which%20has%20worked%20on%20supplying%20Israel's%20Iron%20Dome%20since%202014.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20an%20October%2024%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fool.com%2Fearnings%2Fcall-transcripts%2F2023%2F10%2F24%2Frtx-rtx-q3-2023-earnings-call-transcript%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%3Cspan%3Eearnings%20call%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20RTX%20Corporation%20CEO%20Greg%20Hayes%20said%20that%20the%20defense%20contractor%20stood%20to%20%26quot%3Bbenefit%26quot%3B%20from%20a%20US%20Department%20of%20Defense's%20budget%20increase%20which%20would%20fund%20the%20supply%20of%20weapons%20to%20Israel%20and%20the%20restocking%20of%20weapons%20in%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20really%20across%20the%20entire%20Raytheon%20portfolio%2C%20you're%20going%20to%20see%20a%20benefit%20of%20this%20restocking%2C%26quot%3B%20Hayes%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fool.com%2Fearnings%2Fcall-transcripts%2F2023%2F10%2F24%2Frtx-rtx-q3-2023-earnings-call-transcript%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%3Cspan%3Esaid%20on%20the%20call%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%26quot%3BOn%20top%20of%20what%20we%20think%20is%20going%20to%20be%20an%20increase%20in%20DOD%20top%20line.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20statement%20was%20in%20response%20to%20a%20question%20from%20Kristine%20Liwag%2C%20an%20analyst%20from%20Morgan%20Stanley.%20Liwag%20asked%20how%20quickly%20RTX%20Corporation%2C%20formerly%20known%20as%20Raytheon%20Corporation%2C%20could%20profit%20if%20Congress%20approves%20President%20Biden's%20request%20for%20a%20DoD%20budget%20increase%20in%202024.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BLooking%20at%20this%20request%2C%20you've%20got%20equipment%20for%20Ukraine%2C%20air%20and%20missile%20defense%20for%20Israel%2C%20and%20replenishment%20of%20stockpile%20for%20both%2C%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fool.com%2Fearnings%2Fcall-transcripts%2F2023%2F10%2F24%2Frtx-rtx-q3-2023-earnings-call-transcript%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%3Cspan%3ELiwang%20said%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20this%20seems%20to%20fit%20quite%20nicely%20with%20the%20Raytheon%20Defense%20portfolio.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERepresentatives%20for%20Morgan%20Stanley%20did%20not%20return%20Insider's%20request%20for%20comment.%20A%20representative%20for%20RTX%20Corporation%20declined%20to%20comment%2C%20but%20pointed%20Insider%20to%20Hayes's%20October%2024%20CNBC%20interview%2C%20in%20which%20he%20said%20there%20is%20%26quot%3Bvery%20strong%20demand%26quot%3B%20for%20RTX%20products%20from%20Israel%2C%20the%20US%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bother%20partner%20countries%20around%20the%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BThe%20war%20in%20Gaza%20or%20in%20Israel%2C%20again%2C%20a%20tragic%20situation%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0it%20will%20eventually%20lead%20to%20additional%20orders%2C%20most%20likely%2C%26quot%3B%20Hayes%20said.%20%26quot%3BOur%20focus%20right%20now%20is%20how%20do%20we%20support%20the%20Israeli%20Defense%20Force%3F%20How%20do%20we%20make%20sure%20that%20they%20have%20what%20they%20need%20to%20be%20able%20to%20defend%20their%20country.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fbusiness%2F2023%2F10%2F08%2Fisrael-attack-what-is-the-iron-dome-and-how-does-it-work%2F920a8e92-65d8-11ee-9753-2b3742e96987_story.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%202014%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20RTX%20Corporation%20has%20been%20working%20with%20Israeli%20company%20Rafael%20Advanced%20Defense%20Systems%20to%20help%20produce%20Israel's%20Iron%20Dome%2C%20which%20detects%20and%20shoots%20down%20incoming%20rockets.%20The%20DoD%20has%20been%20funding%20the%20Iron%20Dome%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fbusiness%2F2023%2F10%2F08%2Fisrael-attack-what-is-the-iron-dome-and-how-does-it-work%2F920a8e92-65d8-11ee-9753-2b3742e96987_story.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%3Cspan%3Esince%202011%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20a%20few%20years%20after%20Israel%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2023%2F10%2F09%2Fworld%2Firon-dome-israel-defense-explained-intl-dg%2Findex.html%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520Iron%2520Dome%252C%2520explained%2520and%2520visualized%26amp%3Btext%3DThe%2520Israel%2520Defense%2520Forces%2520said%2Cbatteries%2520were%2520deployed%2520in%25202011.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%3Cspan%3Efirst%20began%20to%20deploy%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E