%20eight-wicket%20defeat%20on%20a%20sluggish%20Chennai%20surface%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20opening%20pair%20of%20Rahmanullah%20Gurbaz%20(65)%2C%20and%20Ibrahim%20Zadran%20(87)%2C%20along%20with%20Rahmat%20Shah%20(77)*%20at%20No.3%2C%20starred%20with%20the%20bat%20to%20help%20Afghanistan%20post%20a%20win%20for%20the%20ages.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EChasing%20283%2C%20a%20challenging%20total%20on%20a%20Chennai%20pitch%20affording%20uneven%20bounce%2C%20Afghanistan%20cantered%20to%20a%20win%20by%20eight%20wickets%2C%20with%20an%20over%20to%20spare.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20the%20post-match%20presentation%20ceremony%2C%20Shahidi%20lauded%20the%20team's%20professional%20approach%20in%20chasing%20down%20the%20target.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20win%20against%20Pakistan%20tastes%20nice.%20The%20way%20we%20chased%20we%20chased%20down%20the%20target...it%20was%20very%20professional.%20We%20are%20looking%20forward%20to%20the%20other%20games.%20We%20believe%20that%20we%20can%20pull%20off%20similar%20chases%20in%20the%20other%20matches%20as%20we%20go%20forward.%20We%20can%20do%20it%20again.%20The%20quality%20and%20brand%20of%20cricket%20we%20have%20been%20playing%20over%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20years%20is%20for%20everyone%20to%20see.%20The%20belief%20was%20there%20as%20well%20while%20we%20were%20playing%20the%20Asia%20Cup%2C%26quot%3B%20Shahidi%20said%20at%20the%20post-match%20presentation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20his%20fellow%20teammates%20were%20eager%20to%20showcase%20their%20skills%2C%20play%20positive%20cricket%20and%20post%20more%20wins%20in%20the%20tournament.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfghanistan%20has%20now%20got%20the%20better%20of%20two%20cricketing%20powerhouses%20--%20former%20world%20champions%20Pakistan%20and%20the%20defending%20champions%20England.%20The%20win%20lifted%20Afghanistan%20to%20sixth%20on%20the%20points%20table.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20the%20start%20of%20the%20tournament%2C%20I%20said%20we%20want%20to%20make%20it%20historic%20for%20our%20country%20and%20fellow%20Afghans.%20We%20beat%20England%2C%20the%20reigning%20world%20champions%2C%20and%20then%20followed%20it%20up%20with%20a%20victory%20over%20Pakistan.%20We%20are%20eagerly%20looking%20forward%20to%20our%20other%20games.%20We'll%20try%20our%20best%20to%20play%20positive%20cricket%20in%20this%20World%20Cup%20and%20bring%20some%20joy%20to%20people%20back%20home%2C%26quot%3B%20Shahidi%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELavishing%20praise%20on%2018-year-old%20spinner%20Noor%20Ahmad%2C%20who%20was%20the%20pick%20of%20the%20bowlers%20for%20Afghanistan%2C%20picking%20up%20three%20wickets%2C%20the%20skipper%20said%20his%20young%20teammate%20came%20up%20with%20an%20%26quot%3Boutstanding%26quot%3B%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20spinners%20came%20good%20today.%20We%20gave%20a%20chance%20to%20Noor%20and%20he%20repaid%20our%20faith%20and%20demonstrated%20his%20talent%20and%20skills%20on%20the%20biggest%20stage.%20Gurbaz%20and%20Ibrahim%20got%20us%20off%20to%20a%20flier%2C%20giving%20us%20momentum%20and%20confidence%20for%20the%20batters%20to%20follow.%20The%20chase%20was%20in%20our%20control%20right%20from%20ball%20one%20to%20the%20end.%20The%20partnership%20that%20myself%20and%20Rahmat%20were%20involved%20in%20ensured%20no%20further%20hiccups%20along%20the%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Afghanistan%20captain%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20high-flying%20Afghans%20will%20play%20Sri%20Lanka%20next%20on%20October%2030%20at%20the%20high-scoring%20Maharashtra%20Cricket%20Association%20Stadium%20in%20Pune.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698199980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F6pj8gk98_hashmatullah-shahidi_625x300_24_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Ftastes-nice-afghanistan-captain-hashmatullah-shahidi-sums-up-stunning-world-cup-victory-against-pakistan-4508491%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Chasing%20283%2C%