%3Cp%3ESpecial%20training%20for%20passengers%20will%20not%20be%20required%2C%20Space%20Perspective%20said.%20All%20they%20have%20to%20do%20is%20sign%20some%20forms%2C%20take%20a%20seat%2C%20and%20strap%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20experience%20is%20meant%20to%20be%20extravagant%20and%20cater%20to%20people%20with%20money%20to%20spend%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsee-the-high-risk-trips-wealthy-travelers-are-booking-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erisk-taking%20adventures%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Christmas-ornament-shaped%20cabin%20is%20built%20with%20a%20space%20toilet%2C%20and%20meals%20and%20cocktails%20will%20be%20served%20during%20the%20flight%2C%20per%20Space%20Perspectives.%20The%20company%20is%20also%20looking%20to%20implement%20design%20elements%20from%20the%20Mercedes-Maybach%20suite%20of%20luxury%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20lot%20that%20goes%20on%20in%20people's%20minds%20when%20they%20think%20about%20how%20we%20fly%20to%20space%2C%26quot%3B%20Poynter%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20wanted%20to%20completely%20reimagine%20this%20for%20people%E2%80%A6%20But%20what%20was%20also%20really%20important%20to%20us%20was%20that%20we%20designed%20the%20interior%20to%20be%20something%20that%20is%20also%20really%20accessible%2C%20and%20approachable.%20So%20it's%20a%20space%20lounge.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMercedes-Maybach%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20company%20also%20said%20Spaceship%20Neptune%20is%20built%20with%20the%20'largest%20windows%20ever%20flown%20to%20space.'%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20purple-lit%20interior%20of%20the%20space%20capsule%2C%20with%20black%20cloth%20seats%2C%20a%20silver%2C%20triangle-shaped%20mini%20bar%2C%20and%20a%20telescope.%20Outside%20the%20large%20windows%20is%20a%20view%20of%20earth%20from%20space%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20s