0also%20in%20an%20arms%20race%20against%20fraud.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20day-to-day%20of%20this%20computational%20war%20might%20not%20be%20as%20dramatic%20as%20Alan%20Turing%20standing%20in%20front%20of%20a%207-foot-wide%20computer%20to%20decipher%20the%20Enigma%20code.%20But%20the%20insurance-fraud%20battle%20follows%20the%20same%20premise%3A%20As%20fraudsters%20use%20new%20tech%2C%20so%2C%20too%2C%20must%20the%20detectors.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20insurers%20agree%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finsurancefraud.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2FArtificial-Intelligence-and-Insurance-Fraud-2020.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%2C%20more%20than%20any%20other%20technology%2C%20will%20be%20the%20game%20changer%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20this%20space%20over%20the%20next%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20driving%20force%20behind%20this%20race%20is%20money%2C%20and%20lots%20of%20it.%20Of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhome.treasury.gov%2Fsystem%2Ffiles%2F311%2F2022%2520Federal%2520Insurance%2520Office%2520Annual%2520Report%2520on%2520the%2520Insurance%2520Industry%2520%25281%2529.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%242.5%20trillion%3C%2Fa%3E%20Americans%20pay%20into%20the%20insurance%20industry%20each%20year%2C%20the%20Coalition%20Against%20Insurance%20Fraud%20estimates%20that%20insurers%20pay%20out%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finsurancefraud.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2FThe-Impact-of-Insurance-Fraud-on-the-U.S.-Economy-Report-2022-8.26.2022.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%24308.6%20billion%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20it%20on%20fraudulent%20claims.%20That%20means%2012%25%20of%20what%20customers%20in%20the%20US%20pay%20is%20funneled%20to%20dishonest%20claimants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELosses%20from%20insurance%20fraud%20are%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.conroysimberg.com%2Fblog%2Finsurance-fraud-costs-the-u-s-308-billion-annually%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DIn%25201995%252C%2520the%2520total%2520amount%2Cthan%2520the%2520CAIF%2527s%2520new%2520estimate.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enearly%20double%20what%20they%20were%2030%20years%20ago%3C%2Fa%3E.%20On%20the%20line%20are%20funds%20that%20could%20otherwise%20go%20toward%20potentially%20life-changing%20payments.%20And%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnewsroom.transunion.com%2Ffraudsters-shift-focus-to-insurance-industry-during-first-half-of-2022%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DFor%2520the%2520second%2520consecutive%2520quarter%2CQ2%25202021%2520and%2520Q2%25202022.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einsurers%20are%20feeling%20the%20heat%20from%20digital%20fraudsters%20far%20more%20than%20other%20online%20industries%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20made%20them%20eager%20to%20use%20their%20counter-fraud%20teams%20to%20see%20what%20else%20AI%20can%20do.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EFraudsters%20are%20using%20AI%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENearly%2060%25%20of%20insurance%20companies%20already%20use%20AI%20such%20as%20machine%20learning%20to%20help%20detect%20regular%20old%20fraud%2C%20let%20alone%20the%20new%20challenge%20of%20fraudsters%20having%20AI%20at%20their%20fingertips%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EScott%20Clayton%2C%20the%20head%20of%20claims%20fraud%20at%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.zurich.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EZurich%20Insurance%20Group%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finsurtechdigital.com%2Finsurtech%2Fshallowfakes-are-the-real-threat-to-the-insurance-industry%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshallowfakes%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20manipulated%20images%20made%20manually%20with%20the%20help%20of%20photo-editing%20software%20%E2%80%94%20keep%20him%20awake%20at%20night.%20But%20a%20flood%20of%20AI-based%20forgeries%2C%20or%20%26quot%3Bdeepfakes%2C%26quot%3B%20is%20another%20threat%20on%20the%20horizon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20kind%20of%20half%20joke%20that%20when%20deepfake%20affects%20us%20significantly%2C%20it's%20probably%20about%20the%20time%20for%20me%20to%20get%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20Clayton%20said.%20%26quot%3BBecause%20at%20that%20point%2C%20I'm%20not%20sure%20that%20we'll%20be%20able%20to%20keep%20pace%20with%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221170%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Scott%20Clayton%20headshot%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65315316be9edfa8eda4d9db%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221172%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EScott%20Clayton%2C%20the%20head%20of%20claims%20fraud%20at%20Zurich%20Insurance%20Group.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Scott%20Clayton%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20this%20isn't%20a%20problem%20of%20the%20future.%20Arnaud%20Grapinet%2C%20the%20chief%20data%20scientist%20of%20Shift%20Technology%2C%20said%20that%20in%20recent%20months%2C%20he's%20seen%20an%20uptick%20of%20deepfaked%20claims%20turning%20up%20in%20his%20data.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20proportion%20doing%20it%20is%20still%20low%2C%20but%20the%20thing%20is%2C%20people%20doing%20it%2C%20they%20do%20it%20at%20scale%2C%26quot%3B%20Grapinet%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.axa.es%2Fdocuments%2F776357%2F26267767%2FNP_XMapa_AXA_fraude_general%2B%25281%2529.pdf%2F480e0f01-56c4-e17d-7cb2-728c0a29ebea%3Ft%3D1679413505451%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAn%20AXA%20Research%20Fund%20study%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20its%20market%20in%20Spain%20found%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsegurosnews.com%2Fnews%2Fla-tasa-de-fraude-al-seguro-en-espana-se-duplica-en-la-ultima-decada-hasta-alcanzar-el-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emost%20fraudulent%20claims%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20for%20real%20incidents%2C%20but%20the%20claimant%20tacks%20on%20exaggerated%20damages.%20These%20opportunistic%20fraudsters%20usually%20fake%20it%20only%20once%20and%20for%20less%20than%20600%20euros%2C%20or%20about%20%24635.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20around%2040%25%20of%20fraud%20is%20premeditated%2C%20and%20these%20cases%20can%20cost%20insurance%20companies%20upwards%20of%20%E2%82%AC3%2C000%2C%20or%20around%20%243%2C170%2C%20according%20to%20the%20study.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20costlier%20category%20is%20where%20deepfakes%20are%20starting%20to%20come%20in.%20Unlike%20the%20one-offs%20committed%20by%20opportunistic%20fraudsters%2C%20those%20who%20use%20deepfakes%20have%20the%20power%20to%20create%20hundreds%20of%20forged%20images.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221509%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Arnaud%20Grapinet%20headshot%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F653152ecbe9edfa8eda4d93e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221131%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EArnaud%20Grapinet%2C%20the%20chief%20data%20scientist%20of%20Shift%20Technology.%3Cp%3EShift%20Technology%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20counter-fraud%20teams%20are%20turning%20to%20software%20development%20kits%20like%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftruepic.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMicrosoft's%20Truepic%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.openorigins.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOpenOrigins'%20Secure%20Source%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20record%20camera%20data%20that%20verifies%20the%20authenticity%20of%20an%20image.%20While%20these%20technologies%20alone%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20detect%20opportunistic%20fraud%2C%20they're%20certainly%20becoming%20part%20of%20the%20modern%20fraud%20investigator's%20tool%20kit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ECurrent%20AI%20tech%20in%20insurance%20delivers%20fraud%20alerts%2C%20and%20GenAI%20additions%20will%20be%20personal%20assistants%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20handlers%20review%20a%20claim%2C%20they%20might%20also%20receive%20an%20alert%20flagging%20suspicious%20activity.%20At%20that%20point%2C%20it's%20passed%20to%20a%20human%20to%20investigate%20whether%20there%20really%20is%20fraud.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20reality%20is%20that%20we're%20still%20relatively%20immature%20in%20terms%20of%20using%20true%20AI%20in%20fraud%20detection%2C%26quot%3B%20Clayton%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20Insurance%20Fraud%20Detection%20Market%20is%20expected%20to%20grow%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reportlinker.com%2Fp06484037%2FInsurance-Fraud-Detection-Market-Size-Share-Analysis-Growth-Trends-Forecasts.html%3Futm_source%3DGNW%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efrom%20%245%20billion%20in%202023%20to%20%2417%20billion%20in%202028%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20programming%20in%20current%20fraud-detection%20systems%20is%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.techtarget.com%2Fsearchenterpriseai%2Ffeature%2FHow-to-choose-between-a-rules-based-vs-machine-learning-system%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erules-based%3C%2Fa%3E.%20If%20an%20insurer%20tells%20the%20program%20a%20particular%20kind%20of%20evidence%20is%20suspicious%2C%20such%20as%20an%20abnormal%20frequency%20of%20uploads%2C%20the%20engine%20knows%20to%20flag%20those%20cases%20to%20investigators.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERules-based%20systems%20are%20a%20relatively%20low%20lift%20for%20developers%20at%20insurance%20companies%20to%20use%20and%20maintain%2C%20but%20it's%20also%20difficult%20to%20add%20new%20rules%20or%20to%20know%20which%20rules%20to%20hard%20code%20in%20the%20first%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%2010%20years%2C%20various%20third-party%20developers%20like%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.friss.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFriss%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ibm.com%2Fdocs%2Fen%2Ffci%2F6.6.x%3Ftopic%3Dfraud-what-is-financial-crimes-insight-claims%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIBM%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.shift-technology.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EShift%20Technology%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20started%20tailoring%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.techtarget.com%2Fsearchenterpriseai%2Ffeature%2FHow-to-choose-between-a-rules-based-vs-machine-learning-system%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emachine-learning%3C%2Fa%3E%20systems%20to%20insurance%20companies.%20Rather%20than%20just%20hard%20coding%20rules%20for%20the%20engine%20to%20follow%2C%20data%20scientists%20can%20show%20it%20thousands%20of%20examples%20of%20fraudulent%20materials%2C%20and%20it%20discovers%20fraudulent%20patterns%20on%20its%20own.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20screenshot%20of%20Shift%20Technology's%20webpage%20interface%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65380d0a0487ff031cad03d3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22923%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EShift%20Technology's%20fraud-detection%20software%20identifies%20and%20highlights%20a%20network%20of%20fraudulent%20claims.%3Cp%3EShift%20Technology%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20Shift%20Technology%20has%20shown%20its%20model%20millions%20of%20materials%20from%20its%20clients%20and%20data%20partners%2C%20such%20as%20claims%2C%20medical%20records%2C%20correspondence%20between%20attorneys%2C%20first%20notice%20of%20loss%2C%20and%20pictures%20of%20damages.%20Representatives%20from%20the%20company%20said%20its%20current%20model%20finds%20three%20times%20more%20fraud%20than%20manual%20or%20rules-based%20tools.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20developers%20are%20working%20to%20apply%20AI%20to%20insurance%20through%20more%20than%20just%20their%20current%20machine-learning%20systems.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGrapinet%20and%20his%20team%20are%20piloting%20a%20generative-AI%20system%20to%20help%20investigators%20with%20tedious%20tasks%20like%20scrutinizing%20100-page%20documents.%20The%20less%20time%20they%20have%20to%20spend%20reading%20records%2C%20the%20more%20they%20can%20spend%20arbitrating%20complex%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EAI%20insurance-tech%20applications%20are%20challenged%20by%20data%20availability%20and%20regulation%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20Shift%20Technology's%20top%20priorities%20is%20adding%20transparency%20to%20their%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20have%20AI%20interacting%20with%20humans%2C%20what's%20very%20important%20is%20explainability%2C%26quot%3B%20Grapinet%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20cannot%20just%20have%20a%20black%20box.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20transparency%20ranks%20among%20insurers'%20top%20concerns%20for%20using%20AI%2C%20it's%20surpassed%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finsurancefraud.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2FArtificial-Intelligence-and-Insurance-Fraud-2020.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eworries%20about%20data%20quality%2C%20lack%20of%20data%2C%20and%20model%20bias%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20any%20given%20insurer%2C%20it's%20very%20difficult%20for%20them%20to%20build%20their%20own%20internal%20fraud%20model%20because%20you%20need%20a%20lot%20of%20data%20for%20AI%20to%20be%20trained%20and%20to%20learn%20and%20to%20improve%20over%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Rob%20Galbraith%2C%20the%20author%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20End%20of%20Insurance%20As%20We%20Know%20It.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221274%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rob%20Galbraith%20headshot%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65315451be9edfa8eda4dc60%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221274%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERob%20Galbraith%2C%20the%20author%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20End%20of%20Insurance%20As%20We%20Know%20It.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EJennifer%20Lindberg%20Studio%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20insurers%20weigh%20their%20appetite%20for%20third-party%20software%20against%20developing%20a%20proprietary%20system%2C%20those%20third-party%20startups%20and%20enterprise%20companies%20are%20leveraging%20their%20ability%20to%20host%20massive%2C%20cross-market%20datasets.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSeeing%20those%20cases%20that%20are%20connected%20to%20not%20just%20a%20single%20insurer%2C%20you're%20not%20going%20to%20see%20that%20stuff%20trusting%20the%2050-year%20grizzled%20insurance%20investigator%20who%20is%20really%2C%20really%20good%20at%20their%20job%2C%20but%20just%20doesn't%20have%20the%20breadth%20to%20see%20all%20of%20that%20that's%20going%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Rob%20Morton%2C%20the%20head%20of%20corporate%20communications%20at%20Shift%20Technology.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20as%20more%20scrutiny%20shifts%20to%20AI%2C%20there%20are%20also%20regulators%20to%20contend%20with.%20Employees%20with%20the%20expertise%20and%20bandwidth%20to%20manage%20data%20compliance%20and%20documentation%20are%20in%20high%20demand.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20there's%20the%20question%20of%20how%20to%20regulate%20third-party%20providers%2C%20and%20the%20insurers%20working%20with%20those%20providers%2C%20especially%20since%20just%20a%20handful%20of%20companies%20might%20become%20tools%20for%20a%20large%20part%20of%20the%20industry.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20still%20a%20very%20evolving%20area%3B%20the%20best%20practices%20aren't%20fully%20set%20in%20stone%2C%26quot%3B%20Galbraith%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20with%20third-party%20models%20and%20proprietary%20models%20alike%2C%20AI%20models%20can%20be%20hard-pressed%20to%20detect%20forms%20of%20fraud%20that%20they%20didn't%20learn%20from%20their%20training%20materials.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20only%20as%20good%20as%20the%20stuff%20we%20know%20about%2C%26quot%3B%20Clayton%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20more%20that%20we%20invest%20and%20t