g%20some%2020%20feet%20away%20from%20Trump%20himself%2C%20who%20sat%20at%20the%20defense%20table.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20the%20most%20part%2C%20Trump%20would%20go%20two-thirds%20into%20the%20meeting%2C%26quot%3B%20Cohen%20added.%20%26quot%3BHe%20would%20just%20show%20up.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3Bgang%26quot%3B%C2%A0%20was%20comprised%20of%20four%20of%20Trump%20Org%20executive%20vice%20presidents%2C%20including%20Cohen%2C%20then%20Trump's%20special%20counsel.%20The%20other%20three%20members%20were%20Matt%20Calamari%2C%20Trump's%20chief%20operating%20officer%2C%20Ron%20Lieberman%2C%20vice%20president%20of%20management%20and%20development%2C%20and%20Allen%20Weisselberg%2C%20the%20chief%20financial%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECohen%20didn't%20speak%20to%20the%20origin%20of%20the%20nickname%20or%20its%20historical%20roots%20during%20his%20testimony.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20nickname%20was%20coined%20by%20an%20Aon%20executive%2C%20he%20said.%20In%20official%20emails%2C%20though%2C%20Aon%20would%20call%20the%20group%20the%20%26quot%3BTeam%20of%20Four%2C%26quot%3B%20a%202013%20email%20that%20was%20moved%20into%20evidence%20showed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20excited%20that%20the%20Trump%20Organization%20has%20created%20a%20Team%20of%20Four%20to%20review%20the%20Trump%20Organization's%20insurance%20program%2C%20insurance%20policy%20buying%20decisions%2C%20claims%20management%20and%20risk%20protection%20protocols%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20Aon%20executive%20told%20the%20gang%20members%20in%20an%20email.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20Cohen's%20testimony%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-cohen-ny-fraud-trial-cage-match-its-on-2023-10%5C%22%3Ehe%20linked%20Trump%20directly%20to%20the%20fraudulent%20net-worth%20statements%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20tasked%20by%20Mr.%20Trump%20to%20increase%20the%20total%20assets%20based%20upon%20a%20number%20that%20he%20arbitrarily%20elected