tt%20House%2C%20built%20in%20the%20late%201920s%20as%20the%20residence%20of%20inventor%20Frank%20A.%20Garbutt%2C%20has%20no%20official%20renters%20or%20current%20leases%2C%20according%20to%20reporting%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.latimes.com%2Fcalifornia%2Fstory%2F2023-10-23%2Fdov-charney-garbutt-house-bankruptcy%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Los%20Angeles%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Still%2C%20seven%20residents%2C%20including%20Charney%2C%20Connor%2C%20and%20Yiannopoulos%2C%20as%20well%20as%20multiple%20former%20American%20Apparel%20employees%2C%20have%20been%20served%20motions%20to%20turnover%20their%20possession%20of%20the%20property%20that%20Charney%20purchased%20for%20%244.1%20million%20in%202006%2C%20when%20American%20Apparel's%20popularity%20was%20booming%2C%20the%20outlet%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20sprawling%2C%2020-room%20estate%2C%20the%20Garbutt%20House%20is%20located%20in%20the%20gated%20Hathaway%20Hills%20Estates%20community%20in%20a%20residential%20neighborhood%20of%20Los%20Angeles.%20Positioned%20above%20the%20surrounding%20cul-de-sacs%2C%20the%20concrete%20compound%20features%20bronze%20accents%2C%20ornate%20tile%2C%20and%20a%20360-degree%20panoramic%20view%20of%20the%20city.%20It%20has%20been%20a%20famous%20filming%20location%20for%20movies%20since%20the%20silent%20era.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20structure%20was%20built%20with%20its%20original%20owner's%20deathly%20fear%20of%20fire%20in%20mind%2C%20the%20Times%20reported.%20Though%20it%20features%20decorative%20carvings%20that%20appear%20to%20be%20made%20from%20wood%2C%20the%20focal%20points%20are%20made%20entirely%20of%20concrete%20and%20bronze%2C%20and%20there%20are%20no%20fireplaces%20on%20the%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EAn%20empire%20on%20fire%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20now%20that%20Charney's%20empire%20has%20come%20crashing%20down%20following%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-apparel-founder-dov-charney-on-sleeping-with-coworkers-2017-9%5C%22%3Eallegations%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20from%20multiple%20women%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20an%20unsuccessful%20%2420%20million%20bid%20to%20try%20to%20re-take%20control%20of%20his%20company%2C%20his%20debtors%20%E2%80%94%20including%20the%20hedge%20fund%20he%20borrowed%20the%20%2420%20million%20from%20%E2%80%94%20are%20trying%20to%20collect.%20But%20they%20aren't%20having%20an%20easy%20time%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20attorney%20for%20Brad%20Krasnoff%2C%20the%20government-appointed%20trustee%20assigned%20to%20oversee%20the%20liquidation%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flos-angeles-apparel-denies-outbreak-after-375-workers-get-covid-2020-7%5C%22%3ECharney's%20assets%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20pay%20his%20debtors%20in%20the%20bankruptcy%20process%2C%20said%20in%20a%20court%20filing%20that%20so%20far%2C%20Krasnoff%20has%20been%20refused%20access%20to%20the%20Garbutt%20House%20property%2C%20despite%20court%20orders%20for%20Charney%20and%20his%20associates%20to%20hand%20it%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECharney's%20legal%20counsel%20has%20tried%20to%20fight%20the%20turnover%20motion%2C%20The%20Times%20reported%2C%20arguing%20that%2017%20liens%20in%20place%20against%20the%20property%20should%20prevent%20the%20trustee%20from%20selling%20it%20because%20the%20sale%20of%20the%20property%20wouldn't%20generate%20enough%20money%20to%20pay%20back%20Charney's%20debts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECharney%2C%C2%A0who%20now%20owns%20Los%20Angeles%20Apparel%2C%20and%20his%20legal%20counsel%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20from%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E'This%20place%20is%20like%20a%20dorm'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20outcome%20of%20whether%20the%20house%20will%20be%20sold%20is%20decided%20in%20court%2C%20the%20trustee%20in%20the%20case%20says%20Charney%2C%20Connor%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmilo-yiannopoulos-fired-from-ye-presidential-team-report-2022-12%5C%22%3EYiannop