ible%2C%20and%20fix%20and%20develop%20China-Bhutan%20friendly%20relations%20in%20legal%20form%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fmprc.gov.cn%2Feng%2Fzxxx_662805%2F202310%2Ft20231023_11166399.html%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E%20put%20out%20by%20the%20Chinese%20foreign%20ministry%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOf%20the%2014%20nations%20with%20which%20China%20shares%20borders%2C%2012%20countries%20have%20settled%20their%20borders.%20Bhutan%20and%20India%20are%20the%20only%20two%20countries%20with%20which%20border%20disputes%20still%20remain.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20statement%2C%20Wang%20Yi%20told%20his%20Bhutanese%20counterpart%2C%20%E2%80%9CChina%20always%20prioritises%20neighbourhood%20diplomacy%20in%20its%20overall%20diplomacy%20and%20adheres%20to%20the%20principle%20that%20all%20countries%2C%20big%20or%20small%2C%20are%20equals.%20China%20respects%20the%20sovereignty%2C%20independence%2C%20and%20territorial%20integrity%20of%20all%20countries%20and%20the%20legitimate%20aspirations%20and%20concerns%20of%20small%20and%20medium-sized%20countries.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Bhutanese%20foreign%20minister%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Chinese%20statement%2C%20said%20Bhutan%20and%20China%20have%20enjoyed%20a%20traditional%20friendship%2C%20and%20Bhutan%20firmly%20abides%20by%20the%20one-China%20principle%20and%20stands%20ready%20to%20work%20with%20China%20for%20an%20early%20settlement%20of%20the%20boundary%20issue%20and%20advance%20the%20political%20process%20of%20establishing%20diplomatic%20relations.%C2%A0He%20also%20thanked%20China%20for%20%E2%80%9Cits%20strong%20support%20and%20assistance%20to%20Bhutan%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20statement%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20both%20countries%20set%20up%20a%20%E2%80%98Joint%20Technical%20Group%E2%80%99%20(JTG)%20on%20the%20delimitation%20of%20the%20China-Bhutan%20boundary%20as%20part%20of%20Beijing%E2%80%99s%20efforts%20to%20speed%20up%20the%20resolution%20of%20the%20boundary%20issue.%20In%20an%20%E2%80%98Expert%20Group%20Meeting%E2%80%99%20(EGM)%20held%20in%20Beijing%20in%20August%2C%20both%20sides%20had%20agreed%20to%20set%20up%20JTG%2C%20and%20to%20take%20%E2%80%9Csimultaneous%20steps%E2%80%9D%20to%20expedite%20the%20implementation%20of%20a%20%E2%80%98three-step%20roadmap%E2%80%99%20that%20will%20lead%20to%20the%20demarcation%20of%20the%20boundary.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EImplications%20for%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EChina%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fbhutan-china-set-up-technical-team-on-delimitation-of-boundary%5C%22%3Easserts%3C%2Fa%3E%20claims%20over%20roughly%20764%20square%20kilometres%20in%20the%20northwestern%20and%20central%20regions%20of%20Bhutan.%20Originally%2C%20the%20dispute%20was%20part%20of%20border%20negotiations%20between%20India%20and%20China.%20However%2C%20direct%20dialogues%20between%20China%20and%20Bhutan%20were%20initiated%20in%201984.%20Since%20then%2C%20over%2024%20rounds%20of%20border%20talks%20and%2012%20rounds%20of%20expert-level%20meetings%20have%20taken%20place%2C%20which%20have%20been%20focusing%20on%20Jakarlung%20and%20Pasamlung%20areas%20in%20north%20Bhutan%2C%20and%20the%20Doklam%20area%20in%20west%20Bhutan.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20and%20China%20were%20locked%20in%20an%20intense%20standoff%20over%20Doklam%20in%202017%20for%20about%20two%20months%20after%20China%20began%20laying%20a%20road%20towards%20the%20strategically%20significant%20Jampheri%20ridge%20line.%20While%20India%20considers%20the%20Doklam%20plateau%20as%20Bhutanese%20territory%2C%20China%E2%80%99s%20stated%20position%20is%20that%20it%20is%20an%20extension%20of%20its%20Chumbi%20Valley%2C%20located%20between%20Sikkim%20and%20Bhutan.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20June%202020%2C%20China%20also%20claimed%20the%20Sakteng%20Wildlife%20Sanctuary%2C%20located%20in%20eastern%20Bhutan%2C%20as%20its%20own.%20The%20region%20also%20shares%20borders%20with%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20in%20India.%20China%20also%20allegedly%20built%20several%20villages%20in%20the%20Bhutanese%20territory%2C%20which%20Bhutan%E2%80%99s%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20Lotay%20Tshering%2C%20had%20dismissed%20in%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fbhutan-india-china-border-lotay-tshering%5C%22%3Einterview%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20the%20Belgian%20newspaper%C2%A0%3Cem%3ELa%20Libre%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0in%20March.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETshering%20had%20said%20that%20the%20demarcation%20of%20the%20Bhutan-China%20boundary%20would%20be%20settled%20at%20an%20early%20date%2C%20but%20the%20tri-junction%20point%20with%20India%20would%20be%20dealt%20with%20separately%20with%20the%20inclusion%20of%20India.%20%E2%80%9CDoklam%20is%20a%20junction%20point%20between%20India%2C%20China%20and%20Bhutan.%20It%20is%20not%20up%20to%20Bhutan%20alone%20to%20fix%20the%20problem.%20There%20are%20three%20of%20us.%20There%20is%20no%20big%20or%20small%20country%3B%20all%20are%20three%20equal%20countries%2C%20each%20counting%20for%20one-third%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tshering%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Bhutanese%20prime%20minister%20had%20also%20said%20discussions%20on%20the%20tri-junction%20can%20only%20start%20once%20India%20and%20China%20have%20resolved%20their%20differences%20along%20their%20borders.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20ready.%20We%20can%20discuss%20this%20as%20soon%20as%20the%20other%20two%20parties%20are%20ready.%20India%20and%20China%20have%20problems%20all%20along%20their%20border.%20We%20are%20waiting%20to%20see%20how%20they%20will%20settle%20their%20differences%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20had%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20India%2C%20Doklam%20holds%20great%20significance%20from%20a%20security%20point%20of%20view.%20China%E2%80%99s%20control%20over%20the%20region%20would%20pose%20a%20threat%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20Siliguri%20Corridor%2C%20a%2022-km%20stretch%20which%20connects%20the%20Indian%20mainland%20to%20the%20Northeast.%20The%20stretch%2C%20commonly%20known%20as%20the%20Chicken%E2%80%99s%20Neck%2C%20links%20India%20with%20Tibet%2C%20Nepal%2C%20Bhutan%2C%20and%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698154823000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F24173057%2FThe-Wire-53.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fchina-bhutan-vow-to-conclude-border-talks-soon-will-have-implications-for-india%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bhutan's%20foreign%20minister%20Tandi%20Dorji%20held%20talks%20with%20Chinese%20foreign%20minister%20Wang%20Yi%20in%20Beijing%20on%20October%2023.%20While%20India%20considers%20the%20strategic%20Doklam%20Plateau%20as%20the%20undisputed%20territory%20of%20Bhutan%2C%20China%20claims%20the%20region%20as%20its%20own.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fchina-bhutan-vow-to-conclude-border-talks-soon-will-have-implications-for-india%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Putin%20'fine'%2C%20Kremlin%20says%20amid%20more%20reports%20of%20illness%20-%20and%20comments%20on%20body%20double%20rumours%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698153780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F10%2F768x432%2Fskynews-vladimir-putin-moscow_6333688.jpg%3F20231024131912%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fvladimir-putin-fine-kremlin-says-amid-more-reports-of-illness-and-comments-on-body-double-rumours-12991661%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Kremlin%20has%20dismissed%20fresh%20speculation%20that%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20is%20ill%20and%20called%20rumours%20that%20he%20uses%20a%20body%20double%20an%20%26quot%3Babsurd%20hoax%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fvladimir-putin-fine-kremlin-says-amid-more-reports-of-illness-and-comments-on-body-double-rumours-12991661%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.am