C%2Fstrong%3E%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%20chief%20Mohan%20Bhagwat%20has%20questioned%20whether%20%E2%80%9Cextremists%20from%20across%20the%20border%E2%80%9D%20were%20among%20those%20behind%20the%20ongoing%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20which%20has%20been%20in%20the%20grip%20of%20ethnic%20violence%20since%20May%203.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20his%20Vijayadashami%20speech%20at%20the%20RSS%20headquarters%20in%20Nagpur%20on%20Tuesday%20(October%2024)%2C%20Bhagwat%20questioned%20%E2%80%9Cforeign%20powers%E2%80%9D%20who%20may%20be%20taking%20advantage%20of%20such%20unrest%20and%20instability%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20we%20look%20at%20the%20current%20situation%20of%20Manipur%2C%20this%20fact%20becomes%20obvious%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rss.org%2FEncyc%2F2023%2F10%2F24%2FVijayaDashami-2023-Speech.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esaid%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CHow%20did%20this%20mutual%20discord%20and%20hatred%20suddenly%20erupt%20in%20Manipur%2C%20which%20had%20been%20peaceful%20for%20almost%20a%20decade%3F%20Were%20there%20extremists%20from%20across%20the%20border%20also%20among%20those%20who%20committed%20violence%3F%20Why%2C%20and%20by%20whom%2C%20was%20an%20attempt%20made%20to%20give%20a%20communal%20tinge%20to%20this%20mutual%20conflict%20between%20the%20Manipuri%20Meitei%20and%20Kuki%20communities%2C%20who%20were%20apprehensive%20about%20the%20future%20of%20their%20existence%3F%20Who%20has%20a%20vested%20interest%20in%20trying%20to%20drag%20and%20besmirch%20an%20organisation%20like%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%2C%20which%20has%20been%20engaged%20in%20serving%20everyone%20without%20any%20bias%20for%20years%2C%20into%20this%20unfortunate%20incident%20without%20any%20reason%3F%20Which%20foreign%20powers%20may%20be%20interested%20in%20taking%20advantage%20of%20such%20unrest%20and%20instability%20in%20Manipur%2C%20located%20between%20Nagabhoomi%20and%20Mizoram%20in%20this%20border%20area%3F%20Does%20the%20geopolitics%20of%20Southeast%20Asia%20also%20have%20a%20role%20in%20these%20events%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EQuestioning%20the%20%E2%80%9Cinstigation%20of%20violence%E2%80%9D%20Bhagwat%20said%20that%20violence%20has%20prevailed%20in%20the%20north%20eastern%20state%20despite%20a%20%E2%80%9Cstrong%20government%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20country%20and%20a%20state%20government%20that%20wanted%20peace%20and%20stability%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CDespite%20there%20being%20a%20strong%20government%20in%20the%20country%2C%20on%20whose%20strength%20and%20instigation%20has%20this%20violence%20continued%20unabated%20for%20so%20many%20days%3F%20Why%20did%20this%20violence%20erupt%20and%20continue%20even%20though%20there%20was%20a%20state%20government%20that%20wanted%20to%20maintain%20the%20peace%20that%20had%20prevailed%20over%20the%20last%209%20years%3F%20Now%2C%20when%20people%20on%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20conflict%20are%20seeking%20peace%2C%20which%20are%20these%20forces%20that%20are%20attempting%20to%20trigger%20hatred%20and%20violence%20by%20causing%20an%20incident%20as%20soon%20as%20any%20positive%20step%20is%20seen%20being%20taken%20in%20that%20direction%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-violence-reasons-failure-and-solution-q-and-a%5C%22%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20Behind%20the%20Manipur%20Violence%20and%20Why%20Stopping%20It%20Poses%20a%20Test%20For%20Modi%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBhagwat%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Cmultidimensional%20efforts%E2%80%9D%20will%20be%20required%20along%20with%20a%20strong%20political%20will%20and%20leadership%20in%20%E2%80%9Cbridging%20the%20gap%20of%20mutual%20distrust%20that%20has%20arisen%20due%20to%20the%20unfortunate%20situation%20between%20the%20two%20communities.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20the%20outbreak%20of%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20on%20May%203%2C%20more%20than%2070%2C000%20people%20have%20been%20displaced%20and%20over%20170%20people%20have%20died.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20government%20under%20chief%20minister%20Biren%20Singh%20has%20come%20under%20the%20scanner%20for%20the%20continued%20violence%20in%20the%20state.%20However%2C%20the%20central%20government%20has%20defended%20Singh%20under%20opposition%20fire%20and%20said%20that%20there%20is%20no%20need%20for%20his%20removal%20as%20he%20has%20been%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Famit-shah-defends-biren-singh-in-parliament%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%9Ccooperative.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20May%203%2C%20violence%20broke%20out%20in%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20Churachandpur%20after%20a%20Kuki-led%20tribal%20solidarity%20march%20in%2010%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%2016%20districts.%20As%20the%20Meitei%20community%20organised%20counter-protests%20and%20blockades%2C%20clashes%20spread%20across%20the%20state.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-violence-reasons-failure-and-solution-q-and-a%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20violence%20was%20initially%20pitted%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20a%20Manipur%20high%20court%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20ruling%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20longstanding%20Meitei%20demand%20for%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20status%2C%20the%20BJP%20government%20in%20the%20state%20in%20recent%20months%20has%20sought%20to%20shift%20the%20blame%20on%20outside%20forces.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20an%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fpolitical-pulse%2Fmanipur-cm-biren-singh-interview-dialogue-top-priority-want-manipuris-to-feel-secure-again-8974021%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20interview%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Singh%20said%20on%20October%209%20that%20the%20violence%20was%20due%20to%20%E2%80%9Cexternal%20forces%E2%80%9D%20affected%20by%20his%20war%20on%20drugs%20and%20illegal%20immigration.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20July%2C%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20news%20agency%20ANI%20as%20well%2C%20Singh%20had%20blamed%20external%20forces%20and%20called%20the%20violence%20%E2%80%9Cpre%20planned.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CManipur%20shares%20its%20borders%20with%20Myanmar.%20China%20is%20also%20nearby.%20As%20much%20as%20398%20km%20of%20our%20borders%20are%20porous%20and%20unguarded.%20There%20are%20security%20forces%20deployed%20on%20our%20frontiers%2C%20but%20even%20a%20robust%20and%20extensive%20security%20deployment%20can%E2%80%99t%20cover%20such%20a%20vast%20area.%20However%2C%20going%20by%20what%E2%80%99s%20happening%2C%20we%20can%20neither%20deny%20nor%20vehemently%20affirm%E2%80%A6it%20seems%20pre-planned%20but%20the%20reason%20is%20not%20clear%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faninews.in%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fpolitics%2Fseems-pre-planned-manipur-cm-biren-singh-hints-at-foreign-hand-behind-violence20230701224931%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esaid%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Finclusion-of-meiteis-in-st-list-rejected-in-1982-2001-historical-documents-kept-from-manipur-hc%5C%22%3EInclusion%20of%20Meiteis%20in%20ST%20List%20Rejected%20in%201982%2C%202001%2C%20Historical%20Documents%20Kept%20From%20Manipur%20HC%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%9CAttempt%20to%20harvest%20votes%20by%20inflaming%20emotions%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBhagwat%20also%20urged%20people%20to%20vote%20wisely%20ahead%20of%20the%20general%20elections%20next%20year.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20country%20is%20going%20to%20hold%20elections%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20in%20the%20early%20days%20of%202024.%20Attempts%20to%20harvest%20votes%20by%20inflaming%20emotions%20are%20not%20desirable%2C%20but%20they%20still%20keep%20happening.%20Let%20us%20avoid%20these%20things%2C%20as%20they%20hurt%20the%20unity%20of%20the%20society.%20To%20cast%20vote%20is%20the%20duty%20of%20every%20citizen%2C%20and%20we%20must%20follow%20it.%20Cast%20your%20vote%20keeping%20in%20mind%20the%20vital%20issues%20of%20unity%2C%20integrity%2C%20identity%20and%20development%20of%20the%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ERam%20Temple%20inauguration%20on%20January%2022%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20his%20speech%2C%20Bhagwat%20also%20announced%20the%20date%20of%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20with%20the%20consecration%20of%20Ram%20Lalla%20idol%20on%20January%2022%2C%202024.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20inauguration%20of%20the%20temple%20just%20months%20ahead%20of%20the%20general%20elections%20due%20in%20May%20next%20year%20holds%20significance%20for%20the%20BJP%20as%20it%20seeks%20a%20third%20consecutive%20term%20in%20the%20government.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20endeavours%20and%20efforts%20of%20a%20nation%20are%20driven%20by%20the%20national%20ideals%20that%20serve%20the%20global%20purpose%20of%20that%20nation.%20Therefore%2C%20a%20temple%20for%20Shri%20Ramlala%2C%20whose%20picture%20is%20depicted%20on%20a%20page%20of%20the%20original%20copy%20of%20our%20constitution%2C%20is%20being%20built%20in%20Ayodhya.%20It%20has%20been%20announced%20that%20Shri%20Ramlala%20will%20be%20consecrated%20in%20the%20sanctum%20sanctorum%20of%20the%20temple%20on%20January%2022%2C%202024%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CDue%20to%20practical%20difficulties%20and%20security%20reasons%2C%20only%20a%20limited%20number%20of%20people%20would%20be%20able%20to%20be%20present%20in%20Ayodhya%20on%20that%20auspicious%20occasion.%20Lord%20Shri%20Ram%20personifies%20dignified%20conduct%20for%20our%20ancient%20nation%2C%20is%20the%20epitome%20of%20dutifulness%20and%20Dharm%2C%20and%20symbolises%20affection%20and%20compassion.%20Same%20type%20of%20environment%20should%20be%20created%20at%20our%20respective%20places.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBhagwat%20added%20that%20the%20RSS%20should%20organise%20events%20to%20commemorate%20the%20occasion%20at%20various%20locations.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELast%20week%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Telegraph%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Fprime-minister-narendra-modis-inauguration-hint-in-ayodhya-call-to-vips%2Fcid%2F1973216%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20citing%20sources%20in%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20government%20that%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fpm-modi-to-unveil-ayodhya-ram-temple-on-jan-22-2024-temple-trusts-appeal-sparks-speculation%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EModi%20could%20offer%20inaugural%20prayers%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20at%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20on%20January%2022.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMonths%20after%20the%202019%20general%20election%2C%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-ayodhya-verdict-possession%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ESupreme%20Court%20in%20November%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20year%20handed%20over%20the%20disputed%20land%20in%20Ayodhya%20%E2%80%93%20where%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20once%20stood%20%E2%80%93%20to%20the%20Hindu%20side.%20The%20court%20also%20ordered%20that%20a%20trust%20be%20formed%20by%20the%20government%20of%20India%20to%20which%20the%20land%20would%20be%20turned%20over%20and%20which%20would%20build%20the%20Ram%20temple%20on%20th