0ancestor%20of%20our%20community%2C%20the%20Asurs%2C%20being%20killed%20by%20Ma%20Durga.%20Many%20in%20the%20older%20generations%20observe%20fasts%20and%20weep%20during%20the%20Durga%20Puja%20festival.%20These%20are%20old%20customs%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20her%20late%2050s%2C%20Bina%20resides%20in%20Nagrakata%20village%20in%20the%20hilly%20region%20bordering%20Bhutan%20in%20West%20Bengal%E2%80%99s%20Jalpaiguri%20district.%20She%20is%20one%20of%20the%20remaining%20members%20of%20the%20Asur%20tribe%20in%20the%20state%2C%20a%20small%20Austroasiatic%20ethnic%20group%20who%20live%20in%20West%20Bengal%2C%20Assam%2C%20Odisha%2C%20Meghalaya%2C%20and%20Jharkhand.%20The%20Asur%20people%20believe%20themselves%20to%20be%20descendants%20of%20Mahishasur%2C%20who%2C%20in%20Hindu%20mythology%2C%20was%20defeated%20by%20the%20goddess%20Durga.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F24133511%2Fimage.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F24133511%2Fimage.png%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F24133511%2Fimage-300x168.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F24133511%2Fimage-1024x574.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681518%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22605%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAn%20elder%20of%20the%20Asur%20community%20in%20Nagrakata%2C%20Bengal.%20Photo%3A%20Joydeep%20Sarkar%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDuring%20the%20five%20days%20of%20Durga%20Puja%2C%20while%20most%20of%20Bengal%20participates%20in%20celebrations%2C%20the%20Asur%20community%20practices%20seclusion%2C%20locking%20themselves%20indoors%20to%20mourn%20the%20slaying%20of%20Mahishasur.%20The%20elders%20of%20the%20community%20say%20that%20this%20mourning%20is%20rooted%20in%20the%20mythical%20fear%20of%20being%20deceived.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20anthropologists%2C%20the%20Asurs%20were%20forced%20to%20leave%20the%20Indus%20Valley%20by%20the%20Aryans%2C%20and%20migrated%20to%20Netarhat%20in%20the%20Chota%20Nagpur%20Plateau%2C%20which%20has%20been%20inhabited%20by%20various%20tribes%20for%20many%20centuries.%20In%20the%2019th%20century%2C%20the%20British%20relocated%20them%20to%20North%20Bengal%20to%20work%20at%20the%20tea%20plantations.%20As%20per%20the%202011%20census%2C%20there%20are%204%2C861%20people%20from%20the%20Asur%20tribe%20currently%20living%20in%20West%20Bengal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20there%20is%20a%20real%20and%20pressing%20fear%20that%20also%20grips%20the%20community%20%E2%80%93%20their%20uncertain%20citizenship%20status.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20in%20great%20danger%2C%20we%20have%20no%20papers.%20I%20went%20to%20the%20tea%20garden%20manager%20who%20employs%20us%20and%20they%20assured%20us%20that%20they%20will%20put%20it%20in%20writing%20that%20we%20have%20been%20working%20for%20many%2C%20many%20years.%20But%20these%20assurances%20do%20not%20hold%20much%20legal%20weight%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bina%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F24133441%2Fimage-2.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22808%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F24133441%2Fimage-2.png%20808w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F24133441%2Fimage-2-300x200.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681516%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22537%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EBina%20Asur.%20Photo%3A%20Joydeep%20Sarkar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EAn%20elderly%20man%20says%20that%20many%20Asurs%20were%20treated%20as%20pariahs%20due%20to%20their%20last%20name%20and%20converted%20to%20Christianity%20to%20escape%20such%20censure.%20He%20also%20cites%20the%20example%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fassam-first-batch-of-foreigners-shifted-to-matia-detention-centre%5C%22%3EAssam%20and%20its%20detention%20camps%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20literacy%20rate%20within%20the%20community%20is%20low%20at%2045%25.%20In%20the%20Dooars%20region%2C%20the%20majority%20of%20Asur%20community%2C%20including%20Bina%2C%20are%20employed%20in%20the%20tea%20estates.%20At%20the%20Carron%20tea%20estate%2C%20all%2053%20houses%20in%20which%20the%20Asurs%20live%20are%20mud%20and%20bamboo%20huts%20with%20tin%20sheds.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20were%20recognised%20as%20a%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20only%20in%202014%2C%20after%20years%20of%20struggle.%20But%20community%20members%20feel%20that%20the%20benefits%20of%20government%20schemes%20are%20yet%20to%20reach%20them.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20many%20years%2C%20we%20have%20been%20hearing%20that%20the%20government%20will%20provide%20houses%20as%20part%20of%20a%20scheme.%20However%2C%20to%20be%20eligible%20for%20a%20house%2C%20one%20must%20have%20the%20land%20registered%20in%20their%20name.%20I%20earn%20Rs%20225%20after%20working%20all%20day%2C%20and%20there%20is%20no%20concept%20of%20savings%20in%20the%20tea%20garden.%20How%20are%20we%20supposed%20to%20buy%20land%20in%20these%20circumstances%3F%E2%80%9D%20asked%20Bina.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20village%2C%20there%20is%20just%20one%20car%2C%20an%20aging%20Tata%20Sumo%2C%20prominently%20displaying%20the%20word%20%E2%80%98JESUS%E2%80%99%20on%20its%20front.%20It%20is%20the%20only%20way%20of%20transporting%20ailing%20individuals%20to%20nearby%20towns%2C%20and%20it%20is%20highly%20valued%20by%20the%20local%20community.%20The%20community-owned%20car%20stands%20as%20a%20symbol%20of%20pride%20and%20is%20parked%20at%20a%20central%20place%20within%20the%20settlement.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F24133425%2Fimage-3.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F24133425%2Fimage-3.png%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F24133425%2Fimage-3-300x170.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F24133425%2Fimage-3-1024x581.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681515%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22613%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20car%20which%20doubles%20as%20an%20ambulance.%20Photo%3A%20Joydeep%20Sarkar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20of%20the%20elder%20members%20of%20the%20community%20reflects%2C%20%E2%80%9COnce%20upon%20a%20time%2C%20our%20ancestors%20were%20defeated%20by%20Ma%20Durga.%20Now%2C%20the%20government%20may%20seek%20to%20displace%20us%2C%20even%20imprison%20us.%20But%20we%20will%20resist%20and%20stand%20our%20ground.%20We%20are%20the%20descendants%20of%20the%20Asur.%20We%20understand%20the%20art%20of%20fighting!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Translated%20from%20the%20Bengali%20original%20by%20Aparna%20Bhattacharya)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698135351000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fupload