-ordered-to-pay-rs-3-000-for-asking-customer-to-buy-rs-20-carry-bag-123102400351_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20a%20Small%20Town%20in%20UP%20Is%20Bridging%20Cultures%20Through%20Ramleela%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F24105818%2Fimage-1419.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Bakshi%20Ka%20Talab%2C%20a%20small%20town%2030%20kilometres%20away%20from%20Lucknow%2C%20the%20call%20of%20%3Cem%3Eazaan%3C%2Fem%3E%20(an%20Islamic%20call%20to%20prayer)%20echoes%20through%20the%20air.%20It%20is%20time%20for%20namaz%2C%20and%20Salman%20Khan%20bows%20down%20with%20devotion.%20He%20completes%20his%20prayer%20and%20dons%20his%20cap.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20the%20adjacent%20area%20is%20abuzz%20with%20the%20rehearsal%20for%20Ramleela%2C%20where%20everyone%20is%20awaiting%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20arrival.%20Khan%20plays%20the%20role%20of%20Lord%20Rama.%20He%20takes%20the%20stage%20to%20act%20in%20a%20scene%20where%20he%20engages%20in%20a%20conversation%20with%20Lord%20Parashuram.%20In%20his%20opening%20dialogue%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EShiv%20dhanush%20todne%20wala%20bhi%2C%20Koi%20Shiv%20pyaara%20hi%20hoga%2C%20Jisne%20aisa%20apraadh%20kiya%2C%20Wo%20daas%20tumhara%20hi%20hoga%3C%2Fem%3E%20(The%20one%20who%20broke%20Lord%20Shiva%E2%80%99s%20bow%2C%20must%20be%20someone%20beloved%20to%20Shiva%3B%20and%20for%20doing%20such%20a%20thing%2C%20that%20devotee%20must%20be%20yours.)%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20past%2051%20years%2C%20the%20Ramleela%20in%20Bakshi%20Ka%20Talab%20has%20been%20breaking%20religious%20barriers%2C%20with%20Khan%20playing%20the%20role%20of%20Lord%20Rama.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20tradition%20was%20started%20in%201972%20by%20the%20then%20gram%20pradhan%2C%20Maikulal%20Yadav%2C%20and%20his%20friend%2C%20Muzaffar%20Hussain.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20Ramleela%2C%20Muslims%20perform%20various%20roles%20such%20as%20Lord%20Rama%2C%20Laxman%2C%20Sita%2C%20Janak%2C%20Dasharath%2C%20and%20many%20others.%20Just%20as%20Khan%20portrays%20the%20character%20of%20Lord%20Ram%2C%20Suhail%20Khan%20takes%20on%20the%20role%20of%20Laxman%2C%20while%20Farhan%20Ali%20portrays%20Sita.%20Bharat%20is%20played%20by%20Suhel%20Khan%2C%20and%20Sher%20Khan%20embodies%20the%20character%20of%20Janak.%20Even%20the%20role%20of%20young%20Ram%20is%20portrayed%20by%20Abdul%20Hasan.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESalman%20Khan%20has%20been%20part%20of%20this%20Ramleela%20for%20the%20last%2012%20years.%20And%20it%20has%20been%20seven%20years%20since%20he%20has%20been%20performing%20on%20stage%20as%20Lord%20Rama.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20wear%20the%20crown%20and%20dress%20as%20the%20king%20of%20Ayodhya%2C%20an%20aura%20of%20devotion%20envelops%20the%20scene.%20People%20feel%20that%20Lord%20Rama%20is%20physically%20present%20before%20them.%20Men%2C%20women%2C%20and%20children%20shower%20flowers%20and%20seek%20blessings%20by%20touching%20my%20feet.%20During%20these%20moments%2C%20people%20seem%20to%20forget%20my%20real%20identity%20and%20perceive%20me%20as%20Lord%20Rama.%20Experiencing%20this%20atmosphere%20fills%20me%20with%20a%20profound%20sense%20of%20divine%20happiness%20and%20makes%20me%20feel%20as%20if%20I%20have%20embodied%20Lord%20Shri%20Ram%2C%20a%20rare%20feeling%2C%20I%20may%20not%20experience%20elsewhere.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20people%20in%20a%20small%20town%20like%20Bakshi%20ka%20Talab%20can%20coexist%20with%20brotherhood%20and%20solidarity%2C%20why%20do%20some%20individuals%20attempt%20to%20spread%20hatred%20across%20the%20entire%20country%2C%E2%80%9C%20says%20Salman%20Khan%2C%20who%20is%20a%20gym%20trainer.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETwenty-year%20old%20Sahil%20Khan%2C%20a%20student%2C%20who%20plays%20the%20role%20of%20Laxman%2C%20joined%20the%20Ramleela%20when%20he%20was%20nine%20years%20old.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20was%20a%20child%2C%20this%20tradition%20piqued%20my%20curiosity.%20Initially%2C%20I%20had%20started%20to%20play%20the%20roles%20of%20Bharat%2C%20Shatrughan%2C%20etc.%2C%20but%20as%20time%20passed%2C%20I%20started%20getting%20more%20important%20roles%2C%20and%20eventually%20got%20to%20play%20the%20role%20of%20Laxman.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThough%20he%20plays%20the%20role%20of%20Laxman%2C%20Sahil%20holds%20Lord%20Ram%20in%20unparalleled%20esteem.%20%E2%80%9CLord%20Ram%20was%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EMaryada%20Puroshottam%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20(embodiment%20of%20the%20ideal%20man)%2C%20who%20did%20not%20bat%20an%20eyelid%20before%20setting%20off%20on%20his%2014-year%20exile%20in%20the%20forest%2C%20in%20pursuance%20of%20his%20father%20Dasharath%E2%80%99s%20wish%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F24110827%2Fimage-1420.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22940%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F24110827%2Fimage-1420.png%20940w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F24110827%2Fimage-1420-300x225.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681495%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22705%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EFrom%20Right%20to%20left%20%E2%80%93%20Suhail%20Khan%20as%20Lakshman%2C%20Salman%20Khan%20as%20Lord%20Ram%2C%20Sujeet%20Yadav%20as%20Suryadev%20and%20Ajay%20Maurya%20(side%20artist).%20Photo%3A%20Bakshi%20ka%20Talab%20Ramleela%20Samiti%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3ESalman%20and%20Sahil%20together%20create%20an%20atmosphere%20that%20unites%20people%20in%20devotion%2C%20transcending%20religious%20barriers.%20%E2%80%9CReligious%20tensions%20between%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims%20are%20increasing%20in%20the%20country%2C%20but%20when%20I%20am%20in%20Bakshi%20Ka%20Talab%2C%20none%20of%20that%20hatred%20is%20perceptible.%20My%20family%20and%20the%20audience%20have%20been%20nothing%20but%20supportive%2C%20showering%20all%20their%20praise%20and%20encouragement%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sahil%20Khan.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThousands%20of%20people%20gather%20to%20witness%20this%20unique%20Ramleela.%20Sanjeev%20Shukla%2C%2055%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Bakshi%20Ka%20Talab%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20was%20a%20child%2C%20my%20father%20used%20to%20bring%20me%20to%20watch%20Ramleela.%20Now%20I%20bring%20my%20son%20to%20watch%20it.%20We%20feel%20a%20great%20sense%20of%20joy%20that%20our%20god%20is%20being%20respected%20and%20played%20by%20the%20people%20from%20other%20faiths%20also.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20director%20of%20this%20Ramleela%20is%20Mohammad%20Sabir%20Khan.%20He%20has%20been%20associated%20with%20it%20in%20various%20capacities%20for%2049%20years.%20He%20started%20directing%20Ramleela%20in%201990.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20child%2C%20I%20used%20to%20watch%20Ramleela%20and%20longed%20to%20be%20part%20of%20it.%20Then%20I%20began%20this%20journey%20with%20the%20role%20of%20Jatayu%20and%20gradually%20started%20directing%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F24112937%2Fimage-1421.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22940%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F24112937%2Fimage-1421.png%20940w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F24112937%2Fimage-1421-300x200.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681496%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22626%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EMohammad%20Sabir%20Khan.%20Photo%3A%20Aman%20Khan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20Sabir%20Khan%20shares%20insights%20with%20this%20scribe%2C%20rehearsals%20are%20underway.%20He%20advises%20Salman%20Khan%20that%20his%20facial%20expressions%20should%20reflect%20Lord%20Ram%E2%80%99s%20calm%20demeanor.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20just%20one%20occasion%20when%20I%20encountered%20some%20objection%C2%A0%20to%20my%20participation%20in%20Ramleela.%20That%20was%20when%20I%20got%20married%2C%20and%20my%20in-laws%20raised%20concerns.%20I%20invited%20them%20to%20see%20our%20Ramleela%20first%20hand%2C%20and%20that%20became%20a%20turning%20point%20for%20them%20as%20they%20watched%20thousands%20of%20people%20applauding%20and%20praising%20my%20performance%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20Ramleela%20has%20seen%20many%20interesting%20phases.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVidesh%20Pal%20Yadav%2C%20son%20of%20Maikulal%20Yadav%2C%20who%20was%20the%20founder%20member%20of%20Ramleela%20organising%20committee%2C%20shares%20an%20interesting%20anecdote.%20%E2%80%9COnce%2C%20Ramzaan%20(the%20holy%20month%20of%20fasting%20for%20Muslims)%20and%20Navratra%20(a%20Hindu%20festival)%20had%20coincided.%20We%20were%20worried%20about%20how%20we%20would%20manage%20Ramleela%20because%20most%20of%20our%20Muslim%20artists%20would%20be%20observing%20Roza%20(fasting)%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20none%20of%20them%20allowed%20their%20fasting%20to%20disrupt%20the%20smooth%20flow%20of%20the%20rehearsals.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9COn%20the%20final%20day%2C%20they%20%5Bthe%20artists%5D%20broke%20their%20fast%20(Iftaar)%20on%20the%20stage%20itself%2C%20just%20before%20starting%20the%20programme%20to%20ensure%20that%20there%20was%20no%20interruption%20in%20the%20performance.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAn%20old%20connection%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20Lucknow%2C%20the%20tradition%20of%20a%20Muslim%20connection%20with%20Ramleela%20has%20deep%20roots.%20In%20the%201780s%2C%20Lucknow%E2%80%99s%20fourth%20nawab%2C%20Asaf-ud-Daula%2C%20donated%206%20acres%20of%20land%20to%20establish%20a%20Ramleela%20ground%20in%20the%20Aishbagh%20locality%2C%20where%20the%20annual%20Ramleela%20has%20been%20held%20ever%20since.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Aditya%20Dwivedi%2C%20secretary%20of%20the%20Aishbagh%20Ramleela%20Samiti%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20renowned%20Ramleela%20in%20India.%20It%20was%20started%20by%20Goswami%20Tulsidas%20in%20the%2016th%20century.%20In%20the%20beginning%2C%20Sadhus%20used%20to%20perform%20Ramleela%20here.%20However%2C%20during%20the%20era%20of%20the%20Nawabs%2C%20many%20Nawabs%20began%20attending%20Ramleela%2C%20and%20they%20were%20so%20fond%20of%20it%20that%20they%20used%20to%20take%20care%20of%20the%20expenses.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEven%20today%2C%20many%20Muslims%20actively%20participate%20in%20the%20Aishbagh%20Ramleela.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F24114245%2Fimage-1422.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22940%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F24114245%2Fimage-1422.png%20940w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F24114245%2Fimage-1422-300x200.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681498%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22626%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAishbagh%20Ramleela.%20Photo%3A%20Aman%20Khan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3ESyed%20Shamshur%20Rahman%20Naved%20has%20been%20the%20dance%20director%20of%20the%20Aishbagh%20Ramleela%20since%202006.%20He%20is%20responsible%20for%20choreographing%20the%20dance%20sequences%20throughout%20the%2010-day-long%20ritual.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDuring%20a%20significant%20scene%20portraying%20the%20marriage%20of%20Lord%20Ram%20and%20Sita%2C%20an%20atmosphere%20of%20joy%20prevails%20as%20Sita%20holds%20the%20%3Cem%3