allegedly%20false%20cases%20against%20the%20community%20and%20those%20who%20raise%20their%20voice.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Ften-years-after-scs-landmark-judgment-dongria-kondhs-in-niyamgiri-still-suffer%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Lotte%20planning%20to%20invest%20Rs%20550%20cr%20to%20expand%20ice%20cream%20business%20in%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698121607000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2016-11%2F28%2Ffull%2F1480354427-4589.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Flotte-planning-to-invest-rs-550-cr-to-expand-ice-cream-business-in-india-123102400148_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20company%20plans%20to%20develop%20a%20state-of-the-art%20manufacturing%20plant%20in%20Maharashtra's%20Pune%20district%20which%20is%20expected%20to%20become%20operational%20by%20June%202024%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A75%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Flotte-planning-to-invest-rs-550-cr-to-expand-ice-cream-business-in-india-123102400148_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Flotte-planning-to-invest-rs-550-cr-to-expand-ice-cream-business-in-india-123102400148_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Flotte-planning-to-invest-rs-550-cr-to-expand-ice-cream-business-in-india-123102400148_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22At%20least%20seven%20dead%20and%20dozens%20injured%20after%20'super%20fog'%20causes%20multiple%20pile-ups%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698095340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F10%2F768x432%2Fskynews-louis