Where%20practical%20knowledge%20was%20imparted%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EChildren%20of%20the%20camp%20were%20taught%20basic%20transactional%20skills%20like%20handling%20money%2C%20attending%20to%20customers%2C%20convincing%20skills%2C%20among%20others.%20For%20this%2C%20a%20%E2%80%98sante%E2%80%99%20was%20held%20where%20they%20would%20sell%20some%20items%20like%20craft%2C%20food%2C%20games%20and%20greeting%20cards%20to%20parents%2C%20teachers%20and%20friends%20who%20dropped%20in.%20The%20parents%2C%20mostly%20mothers%2C%20and%20grandparents%20used%20to%20pitch%20in%20as%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20last%20day%20of%20the%20camp%2C%20an%20exhibition%20would%20be%20organised%20for%20the%20parents%20where%20they%20could%20see%20what%20their%20children%20had%20been%20doing%20during%20the%20camp.%20A%20two-hour%20performance%20by%20the%20students%20would%20be%20followed%20with%20tea%20and%20snacks%20for%20everyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20how%20did%20an%20MS%20patient%20manage%20to%20do%20all%20this%3F%20Ask%20her%20and%20Sudha%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CAll%20you%20need%20is%20courage%20and%20support%20from%20the%20family.%E2%80%9D%20She%20is%20immensely%20grateful%20to%20her%20husband%20who%20took%20such%20good%20care%20of%20her%20down%20the%20years%2C%20without%20a%20single%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESudha%20lost%20her%20husband%20to%20cancer%20a%20decade%20ago.%C2%A0%20The%20couple%20has%20no%20children.%20%E2%80%9CDespite%20all%20that%20she%20has%20gone%20through%2C%20she%20has%20a%20ready%20smile%20for%20everyone%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Jayashree.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMamtha%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CShe%20taught%20us%20to%20delegate%20work%20and%20encouraged%20us%20to%20think%20of%20it%20as%20%E2%80%98our%20camp%E2%80%99.%20We%20all%20learnt%20a%20lot%20from%20this%20endeavour%20of%20hers.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20after%20almost%20three%20decades%2C%20some%20of%20the%20students%20share%20their%20fond%20memories%20of%20the%20summer%20camps.%