%20how%20hypocritical%20I%20was%3B%20not%20practising%20what%20I%20was%20preaching.%20I%20had%20been%20studying%20medicine%20for%20almost%2015%20years%20but%20had%20forgotten%20to%20take%20care%20of%20my%20health%20in%20the%20process.%20I%20tried%20every%20diet%20but%20nothing%20worked%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20he%20started%20a%20research%20programme%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F327558%2Frevant-himatsingka-foodpharmer-shares-how-to-read-food-labels-for-health-risks%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eintermittent%20fasting%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20a%20few%20of%20his%20patients%20who%20had%20fatty%20liver.%20As%20the%20programme%20progressed%2C%20the%20doctor%20also%20started%20practising%20the%20same%20in%20his%20personal%20life.%20After%20losing%20almost%2025%20kg%2C%20he%20wanted%20to%20share%20the%20lessons%20he%20learned%20with%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20doctor%2C%20I%20had%20such%20a%20tough%20time%20losing%20weight.%20I%20wondered%20how%20tough%20it%20is%20for%20non-medical%20people.%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%20I%20started%20making%20reels%20on%20Instagram%20to%20help%20people%20learn%20healthy%20habits%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDr%20Pal%20delivers%20these%20important%20messages%20%E2%80%94%20about%20gut%20health%2C%20fatty%20liver%2C%20heart%20health%2C%20foods%20to%20consume%2C%20and%20tips%20for%20a%20healthy%20lifestyle%20%E2%80%94%20with%20a%20comic%20element.%20To%20help%20deliver%20the%20message%20better%2C%20he%20created%20some%20imaginary%20characters%20like%20%E2%80%98Saravana%20Kumar%E2%80%99%20who%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20like%20following%20a%20diet.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Eat%20between%20sunrise%20and%20sunset%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fr