r%20some%20time%2C%20and%20also%20due%20to%20the%20popularity%20of%20the%20video%2C%20I%20get%20a%20lot%20of%20calls%20from%20buyers%20from%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20country.%20So%2C%20say%20a%20person%20from%20Karnataka%20wants%20to%20buy%20%3Cem%3Ekulhads%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20I%20will%20locate%20the%20plant%20set%20up%20in%20Karnataka%20and%20connect%20the%20two.%20This%20way%20the%20customer%20gets%20the%20product%20faster%20and%20without%20any%20damages%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShobhit%20has%20set%20up%20over%2045%20%3Cem%3Ekulhad%20%3C%2Fem%3Eplants%20across%20India%20in%20states%20including%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20Karnataka%20etc.%20He%20is%20also%20setting%20up%20one%20plant%20in%20Canada%20which%20will%20be%20launched%20in%20January%20next%20year.%20By%20setting%20up%20plants%20in%20different%20states%2C%20he%20has%20formed%20a%20network%20of%20%3Cem%3Ekulhad-%3C%2Fem%3Emakers%20across%20the%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ENot%20his%20first%20attempt%20at%20business%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3ELooking%20back%2C%20Shobhit%20informs%20that%20he%20has%20tried%20his%20hand%20at%20various%20types%20of%20businesses%20before%20finding%20success%20with%20Mittisa.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20was%20in%20college%2C%20I%20started%20a%20course%20where%20I%20taught%20students%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F85389%2Fwhy-effective-communication-can-make-big-difference%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20communication%20skills%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20earned%20a%20turnover%20of%20Rs%2022%20lakhs%20in%20a%20year.%20Then%2C%20I%20started%20an%20AI%20company%20but%20it%20had%20to%20be%20shut%20down%20due%20to%20a%20dispute%20among%20the%20co-founders%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThen%20there%20was%20the%20%3Cem%3Echai%20%3C%2Fem%3Ebusiness%20before%20I%20started%20the%20%3Cem%3Ekulhad%20%3C%2Fem%3Ebusiness.%20You%20never%20know%20what%20would%20hit%20the%20right%20nerve%20in%20the%20market%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESomething%20as%20simple%20as%20%3Cem%3Ekulhad%20%3C%2Fem%3Ehas%20helped%20Shobhit%20to%20earn%20crores%20while%20making%20a%20sustainable%20and%20eco-friendly%20product.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fkulhad-1-1697721886.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22With%20his%20kulhad%20business%2C%20Shobhit%20makes%20a%20whopping%20turnover%20of%20Rs%202.76%20crore%20per%20year%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fkulhad-1-1697721886.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fkulhad-1-1697721886-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fkulhad-1-1697721886-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fkulhad-1-1697721886-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fkulhad-1-1697721886-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-332626%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWith%20his%20kulhad%20business%2C%20Shobhit%20makes%20a%20whopping%20turnover%20of%20Rs%202.76%20crore%20per%20year.%C2%A0Picture%20credit%3A%20Shobhit%20Soni%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNo%20other%20cup%20%E2%80%94%20be%20it%20paper%20or%20glass%20%E2%80%94%20is%20as%20sustainable%20and%20eco-friendly%20as%20a%20clay%20cup.%20Even%20when%20we%20started%20our%20chai%20business%2C%20I%20was%20sure%20that%20I%20wanted%20to%20use%20%3Cem%3Ekulhads%20%3C%2Fem%3Eto%20serve%20the%20tea.%20With%20a%20network%20of%20%3Cem%3Ekulhad%20%3C%2Fem%3Emakers%20in%20various%20parts%20of%20the%20country%2C%20businesspersons%20will%20have%20an%20alternative%20to%20run%20their%20business%20eco-consciously%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFound%20Shobhit%E2%80%99s%20business%20idea%20interesting%3F%20You%20can%20reach%20him%20at%207300005969%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande)%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697723243000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D332610%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ajmer-resident%20Shobhit%20Soni%20always%20wanted%20to%20start%20his%20own%20company%20which%20would%20be%20both%20sustainable%2C%20and%20profit-making.%20He%20founded%20Mittisa%2C%20a%20brand%20that%20makes%20traditional%20kulhads%20(clay%20cups)%20and%20sells%20them%20across%20the%20country.%20He%20has%20also%20helped%20set%20up%20more%20than%2045%20kulhad%20plants%20across%20different%20states%20to%20promote%20the%20use%20of%20these%20eco-friendly%20glasses.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332610%2Frajasthan-software-engineer-earns-crores-by-making-traditional-kulhad-business-chai-tea%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%225%20Indians%20Innovating%20With%20Millets%20to%20Make%20Them%20Appealing%20%26amp%3B%20Help%20Farmers%20Earn%20Big%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMillets%20are%20a%20superfood%20that%20are%20rich%20in%20protein%20and%20offer%20a%20plethora%20of%20benefits%20to%20the%20farmers%20who%20grow%20them%2C%20and%20to%20the%20people%20who%20consume%20them.%20India%20is%20the%20top%20producer%20of%20these%20sustainable%20grains%20that%20are%20a%20good%20source%20of%20essential%20nutrients.%20This%20year%20is%20the%20International%20Year%20of%20Millets%2C%20and%20the%20Food%20and%20Agriculture%20Organisation%20(FAO)%20of%20the%20United%20Nations%2C%20is%20creating%20awareness%20about%20millets%20as%20affordable%20foods%20that%20contribute%20to%20a%20healthy%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhat%20differentiates%20millets%20is%20the%20fact%20that%20they%20thrive%20in%20harsh%20growing%20conditions%20and%20are%20climate%20resilient.%20They%20require%20much%20less%20water%20than%20grains%20like%20rice%20and%20wheat.%20The%20FAO%20says%20that%20millets%20provide%20antioxidants%2C%20minerals%2C%20fibre%2C%20iron%20and%20protein%2C%20alongside%20being%20gluten-free%20with%20a%20low-glycaemic%20index.%20They%20are%20also%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F325105%2Fhyderabad-entrepreneur-raju-bhupati-makes-affordable-troo-good-millet-snacks%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeconomical%20for%20farmers%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20they%20require%20less%20water%20and%20fewer%20pesticides%2C%20becoming%20a%20boon%20to%20small%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMillets%20are%20India%E2%80%99s%20traditional%20food%20grain%2C%20grown%20across%20the%20country.%20They%20were%20sidelined%20over%20the%20years%2C%20but%20now%20the%20focus%20is%20squarely%20back%20on%20how%20one%20can%20use%20these%20grains%20in%20their%20diet%20and%20farmers%20are%20switching%20back%20to%20growing%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20forefront%20of%20this%20change%20are%20Indians%20who%20are%20bringing%20millets%20back%20to%20the%20spotlight%20through%20their%20innovations.%20They%20are%20delivering%20millets%20in%20new%2C%20interesting%20ways%2C%20helping%20thousands%20of%20farmers%20along%20the%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHere%20are%20five%20Indians%20championing%20the%20humble%20grain%20through%20their%20startups%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Col%3E%20%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EVeer%20Shetty%20Biradar%2C%20SS%20Bhavani%20Foods%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Fol%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%2